question.text: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited yet?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum masuk?

detailed.en: If your top-up hasn't been credited yet, you only need to upload the receipt once and wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm. If you upload the same receipt twice, the system may reject the transaction and it will take longer to process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it still hasn't been credited, you should send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Please be patient, the system will process it as quickly as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum masuk, anda hanya perlu memuat naik resit sekali sahaja dan tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika anda memuat naik resit yang sama dua kali, sistem mungkin akan menolak transaksi dan ia akan mengambil masa lebih lama untuk diproses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum masuk, anda perlu menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Mohon bersabar, sistem akan memprosesnya secepat mungkin!

question.text: Saya ingin tahu mengapa kemenangan J3 saya belum masuk ke dalam akaun saya.
variations: Kenapa kemenangan saya belum diterima?
Adakah kemenangan J3 saya akan masuk?
Bila kemenangan saya akan diproses?

languages.ms: Saya ingin tahu mengapa kemenangan J3 saya belum masuk ke dalam akaun saya.

detailed.en: If your J3 winnings have not been credited yet, it usually takes between 5 to 30 minutes to process. If it still hasn't appeared after that time, please wait a moment or contact support with your transaction details. We hope it gets resolved quickly!
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan J3 anda belum masuk, biasanya ia akan diproses dalam masa 5 hingga 30 minit. Jika selepas itu masih tiada, sila tunggu sekejap atau hubungi sokongan langsung dengan butiran transaksi anda. Semoga cepat selesai!

question.text: What are the details of the recent win in the Kuda game?

languages.en: What are the details of the recent win in the Kuda game?

detailed.en: Congratulations! You have won RM5,600.00 in the Kuda game with a strike of 7360.

question.text: Why is there a delay in the payout process, boss?

languages.en: Why is there a delay in the payout process, boss?
languages.ms: Kenapa lewat payout boss?

detailed.en: The delay in payout is usually due to the system processing being slower than usual. If your winnings have not been credited within 1-10 minutes, please be patient as the system is processing your transaction. If it takes longer than expected, feel free to contact our live chat support for further clarification.
detailed.ms: Kelewatan payout biasanya disebabkan oleh proses sistem yang mungkin lebih lambat dari biasa. Jika kemenangan anda belum dikreditkan dalam masa 1-10 minit, sila bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses transaksi anda. Jika ia mengambil masa lebih lama dari yang dijangkakan, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi sokongan live chat kami untuk penjelasan lanjut.

question.text: Is the winner report delayed, boss? It's 9 PM.

languages.en: Is the winner report delayed, boss? It's 9 PM.
languages.ms: Adakah laporan pemenang lambat, bos? Sekarang pukul 9 malam.

detailed.en: The winnings for bets J2 and J3 (as per Jaguar 9 PM) will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM to see the credit. If you are using IBOX, the process may take a little longer. If after the waiting period your winnings are still not credited, please contact live chat with a screenshot of your transaction for further verification. Thank you for your patience, boss!
detailed.ms: Kemenangan untuk pertaruhan J2 dan J3 (seperti pada Jaguar 9 malam) akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam wallet anda. Sila semak bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM hingga 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Jika anda menggunakan IBOX, proses mungkin mengambil sedikit masa lebih lama. Jika selepas tempoh menunggu kemenangan anda masih belum dikreditkan, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda untuk pengesahan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda, bos!

detailed.en: Congratulations! The recent lottery win was from Magnum with the strike number 2097, resulting in a total win of RM7,080.00.

question.text: What should I do after topping up using Fast Payment (FPX)?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up using Fast Payment (FPX)?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas topup menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX)?

detailed.en: After topping up using Fast Payment (FPX), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, the funds will be credited within 1-10 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds have not been credited, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas topup menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), sila tunggu selama 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, dana akan dikreditkan dalam masa 1-10 minit. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan dana belum dikreditkan, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan.

question.text: What are the details of the Magic Box prize I won?

languages.en: What are the details of the Magic Box prize I won?
languages.ms: Apakah butiran hadiah Magic Box yang saya menangi?

detailed.ms: Tahniah! Anda telah memenangi Magic Box. Butiran kemenangan adalah seperti berikut: Padang Menang: Magnum, Nombor Menang: 3751, Huruf Menang: L, Jumlah Kemenangan: RM355.00.

question.text: Why hasn't the payment for my Jaguar 3 winnings been credited yet?
variations: Why is my Jaguar 3 win not paid yet?

languages.en: Why hasn't the payment for my Jaguar 3 winnings been credited yet?
languages.ms: Mengapa pembayaran untuk kemenangan Jaguar 3 saya belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: Your Jaguar 3 winnings will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Reports' section between 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM to see the credit. Thank you for your patience, and may you have great luck!
detailed.ms: Kemenangan Jaguar 3 anda akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Laporan' antara 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda, dan semoga anda dapat HUAT yang besar!

question.text: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas berjaya memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: After successfully uploading the receipt, please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Selepas berjaya memuat naik resit, sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin akan melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: I have won on ibox J2 J3, but the winnings have not yet been credited to my account.

languages.en: I have won on ibox J2 J3, but the winnings have not yet been credited to my account.
languages.ms: Saya telah menang di ibox J2 J3, tetapi kemenangan belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya.

detailed.en: If your J3 winnings have not been credited yet, please wait around 10 minutes for the system to process it. Duit menang akan masuk ke wallet anda secara automatik, jadi sila semak dalam aplikasi dari semasa ke semasa.

languages.en: What should I do if I have won in Jaguar 3 and want to know about my winnings?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya telah menang dalam Jaguar 3 dan ingin tahu tentang kemenangan saya?

detailed.en: You need to submit the correct amount again. The correct amount to submit is RM24 instead of RM25. Thank you for your understanding.
detailed.ms: Anda perlu menghantar jumlah yang betul semula. Jumlah yang betul untuk dihantar adalah RM24 dan bukannya RM25. Terima kasih atas pemahaman anda.

question.text: What should I do if my J3 winnings have not been credited to my wallet yet?
variations: What happens if my J3 winnings are not showing up?

languages.en: What should I do if my J3 winnings have not been credited to my wallet yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan J3 saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: If you have won J3, the winnings will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Reports' section between 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM to see the credit. Thank you for your patience, and may you have great luck!

question.text: What should I do if my deposit status shows as PENDING?
variations: Why is my deposit still pending?
How long does it take for a deposit to process?

languages.en: What should I do if my deposit status shows as PENDING?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status deposit saya menunjukkan PENDING?

detailed.en: If your deposit status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing it. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the status is still pending, you can contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika status deposit anda menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memprosesnya. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih PENDING, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

variations: mana Duit kena j23 tak masuk2

languages.en: Why hasn't my winnings from J3 been credited yet?
languages.ms: mana Duit kena j23 tak masuk2

detailed.en: If your 4D number wins, the system will automatically credit the winnings to your wallet shortly. You can check the results by opening the JOKER App, tapping the 4D icon, selecting the Results menu, and comparing the numbers with your receipt. If there are any issues or delays, please send your receipt and results to us for verification.
detailed.ms: Kalau nombor 4D anda kena, sistem akan auto masuk duit menang ke wallet dalam masa yang singkat. Anda boleh semak keputusan dengan membuka App JOKER, menekan ikon 4D, memilih menu Keputusan, dan membandingkan nombor dengan resit anda. Jika ada masalah atau lambat masuk, sila hantar resit dan keputusan kepada kami untuk semakan.

languages.en: What are the chances of winning in a lottery or 4D game?
languages.ms: Apakah peluang untuk menang dalam permainan loteri atau 4D?

detailed.en: Congratulations on your win! The chances of winning in a lottery or 4D game can vary greatly depending on the specific game rules and the number of participants. Generally, the odds are quite low, but winning can lead to significant rewards.
detailed.ms: Tahniah atas kemenangan anda! Peluang untuk menang dalam permainan loteri atau 4D boleh berbeza-beza bergantung kepada peraturan permainan tertentu dan bilangan peserta. Secara amnya, peluangnya agak rendah, tetapi kemenangan boleh membawa kepada ganjaran yang besar.

question.text: What should I do if the deposit amount does not match the receipt?
variations: What to do if my deposit amount is incorrect?
How can I resolve a discrepancy in my deposit?

languages.en: What should I do if the deposit amount does not match the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika jumlah deposit tidak sepadan dengan resit?

detailed.en: To resolve the issue of the deposit amount not matching the receipt, ensure that the amount entered is exactly as stated on the receipt. If there is a discrepancy, such as 'missing one number', please check the transaction details in your banking app. If the problem persists, contact customer support with a screenshot of your transaction for further investigation. If anything is unclear, let me know!
detailed.ms: Untuk menyelesaikan masalah jumlah deposit yang tidak sepadan dengan resit, pastikan jumlah yang dimasukkan adalah tepat seperti yang tertera pada resit. Jika ada perbezaan, seperti 'kurang satu nombor', sila semak butiran transaksi dalam aplikasi perbankan anda. Jika masalah masih berterusan, hubungi sokongan pelanggan dengan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda untuk siasatan lanjut. Jika ada yang tidak jelas, beritahu saya!

question.text: What should I do if my winnings from betting have not been credited to my wallet?
variations: How long does it take for my betting winnings to appear in my wallet?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings from betting have not been credited to my wallet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya dari pertaruhan belum dikreditkan ke dompet saya?

detailed.en: Hi boss, the winnings from betting will be credited to your wallet automatically within 24 hours on the same day. Please be patient as the system is processing. If it has not been credited after 24 hours, you can contact us via live chat for verification. Thank you for your patience!

question.text: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
variations: topup
How to top up using ATM?

languages.en: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top up akaun saya menggunakan ATM?

detailed.en: To top up using an ATM, follow these steps: 1. Go to any bank ATM that supports interbank transfers. 2. Select the 'Transfer' or 'Money Transfer' menu. 3. Enter our company account number (refer to the top-up page in the app). 4. Enter the top-up amount (Minimum RM10). 5. Confirm the transaction and keep the receipt. 6. Take a picture of the receipt and upload it to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat. 7. The top-up will be processed within 3-10 minutes. Ensure the receipt is clear and complete to avoid rejection. If you have any issues or need assistance, reply to us in live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk top up menggunakan ATM, ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Pergi ke ATM mana-mana bank yang menyokong pemindahan antara bank. 2. Pilih menu 'Transfer' atau 'Pemindahan Wang'. 3. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat kami (rujuk halaman top-up dalam aplikasi). 4. Masukkan amaun top-up (Min RM10). 5. Sahkan transaksi dan simpan resit. 6. Ambil gambar resit dan muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan dalam live chat. 7. Top-up akan diproses dalam 3-10 minit. Pastikan resit jelas dan lengkap untuk mengelakkan penolakan. Jika ada masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas kepada kami dalam live chat.

detailed.ms:
Jika anda menghadapi masalah dengan pautan yang tidak berfungsi untuk memuat turun, anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut:

1. **Salin pautan**: Salin pautan yang diberikan dan tampalkannya ke dalam bar alamat pelayar web anda.
2. **Tekan 'Enter'**: Setelah menampal, tekan 'Enter' untuk memulakan muat turun.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited to my account after the expected processing time?
variations: top ul x masuk

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited to my account after the expected processing time?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya tidak masuk ke dalam akaun selepas waktu pemprosesan yang dijangkakan?

detailed.en: After uploading your receipt, the system usually takes 3-10 minutes to process the top-up. If the funds still haven't arrived after that period, please check whether you used ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX). If you used FPX and it takes more than 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of your transaction through live chat for further verification. Additionally, if you have topped up via FPX, please wait 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, it should be credited within 1-10 minutes. If it still hasn't arrived after 10 minutes, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas anda muat naik resit, biasanya sistem memerlukan 3-10 minit untuk memproses top-up. Jika selepas tempoh itu dana masih belum masuk, sila semak sama ada anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Pembayaran Pantas (FPX). Jika menggunakan FPX dan ia mengambil masa lebih dari 10 minit, sila hantarkan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda melalui live chat untuk pengesahan lanjut. Selain itu, jika anda telah top-up melalui FPX, sila tunggu 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, ia akan masuk dalam 1-10 minit. Jika masih belum masuk selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan.

question.text: What are the options for withdrawing winnings of 100k?

detailed.ms: Jika anda menang dengan nombor 100k, anda mempunyai beberapa pilihan untuk pengeluaran: 1. **Pemindahan Langsung**: Anda boleh mengeluarkan jumlah penuh secara langsung (proses biasanya mengambil masa 5-30 minit). 2. **Pengeluaran Sebahagian**: Anda boleh membahagikan pengeluaran kepada jumlah yang lebih kecil untuk lebih fleksibiliti. 3. **Menggunakan Akaun Syarikat**: Untuk kemenangan di atas 100k, anda boleh memilih untuk menggunakan akaun syarikat untuk 'mencuci' dana, yang memudahkan pemprosesan untuk jumlah besar.

detailed.en: If you mistakenly entered the wrong ID while sharing credits, the system cannot automatically return them. Please provide the incorrect JOKER ID you shared and the amount of credits involved. We will try to contact the owner of that ID and ask them to return the credits in the same way (Share Credit). Kami akan cuba menghubungi pemilik ID tersebut dan meminta mereka untuk mengembalikan kredit dengan cara yang sama (Kongsi Kredit). Namun, tiada jaminan bahawa kredit boleh dikembalikan, ia bergantung kepada pemilik ID yang menerimanya. Pada masa akan datang, pastikan ID yang dimasukkan adalah betul sebelum menekan hantar.

question.text: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
variations: topup
how to top up using ATM

languages.en: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top up akaun saya menggunakan ATM?

detailed.en: To top up using an ATM, follow these steps: 1. Go to any bank ATM that supports interbank transfers. 2. Select the 'Transfer' or 'Money Transfer' menu. 3. Enter our company account number (refer to the top-up page in the app). 4. Enter the top-up amount (Min RM10). 5. Confirm the transaction and keep the receipt. 6. Take a picture of the receipt and upload it to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat. 7. The top-up will be processed within 3-10 minutes. Ensure the receipt is clear and complete to avoid rejection. If you have any issues or need assistance, reply to us in live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk top-up menggunakan ATM, ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Pergi ke ATM mana-mana bank yang menyokong pemindahan antara bank. 2. Pilih menu 'Transfer' atau 'Pemindahan Wang'. 3. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat kami (rujuk halaman top-up dalam aplikasi). 4. Masukkan amaun top-up (Min RM10). 5. Sahkan transaksi dan simpan resit. 6. Ambil gambar resit dan muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan dalam sembang langsung. 7. Top-up akan diproses dalam 3-10 minit. Pastikan resit jelas dan lengkap untuk mengelakkan penolakan. Jika ada masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas kepada kami dalam sembang langsung ya.

detailed.en: If the J3 result is delayed today, don't worry. The results and prizes will still be released to the winners. The estimated time for the results is as follows: J2 3PM & J3 3PM â†’ 3:30PM - 4:00PM, J2 9PM & J3 9PM â†’ 9:30PM - 10:00PM, Perdana 3PM & Lucky 3PM â†’ 4:00PM - 4:30PM, Perdana 7PM & Lucky 7PM â†’ 8:00PM - 8:30PM. Sometimes results may be slightly late, but all prizes will be credited as usual. Thank you for your patience! If the result is still empty, it may be a temporary issue. You can try the following steps: refresh or restart the app and try again, switch your internet connection (from WiFi to mobile data or vice versa), clear the app cache if you still cannot see the results. If the problem persists, please contact us via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika keputusan J3 lambat keluar hari ini, jangan risau. Keputusan dan hadiah tetap akan dikeluarkan kepada pemenang. Waktu anggaran untuk pengeluaran keputusan adalah seperti berikut: J2 3PM & J3 3PM â†’ 3:30PM - 4:00PM, J2 9PM & J3 9PM â†’ 9:30PM - 10:00PM, Perdana 3PM & Lucky 3PM â†’ 4:00PM - 4:30PM, Perdana 7PM & Lucky 7PM â†’ 8:00PM - 8:30PM. Kadang-kadang keputusan mungkin sedikit lewat, tetapi semua hadiah akan dikreditkan seperti biasa. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda! Jika keputusan masih kosong, mungkin ada masalah sementara. Anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut: segarkan atau mulakan semula aplikasi dan cuba lagi, tukar sambungan internet (WiFi ke data mudah alih atau sebaliknya), kosongkan cache aplikasi jika anda masih tidak dapat melihat keputusan. detailed.en: If you win in Mega, the winnings will automatically be credited to your JOKER wallet after you exit the game. If it is not there, there may be a delay. Check your wallet history, and if it is still not there, send a screenshot to us. We will help resolve it quickly!
detailed.ms: Jika anda menang di Mega, kemenangan akan secara automatik masuk ke dalam wallet JOKER anda selepas anda keluar dari permainan. Jika tidak ada di sana, mungkin ada kelewatan. Semak sejarah wallet anda, dan jika masih tiada, hantar tangkapan skrin kepada kami. Kami akan bantu selesaikan dengan cepat!

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas berjaya memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: After successfully uploading the receipt, please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Selepas berjaya memuat naik resit, sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin akan melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: What should I do if my payment via Fast Payment (FPX) has not been processed after 10 minutes?

languages.en: What should I do if my payment via Fast Payment (FPX) has not been processed after 10 minutes?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pembayaran saya melalui Fast Payment (FPX) belum diproses selepas 10 minit?

detailed.en: If you have topped up via Fast Payment (FPX), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, the payment should be completed within 1-10 minutes. If it has not been processed after 10 minutes, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah topup melalui Fast Payment (FPX), sila tunggu selama 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, pembayaran akan selesai dalam 1-10 minit. Jika ia belum diproses selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk semakan.

question.text: What are the details of the recent Toto lottery win?
variations: Can you provide information about the Toto lottery results?
What was the winning amount for the Toto lottery?

languages.en: What are the details of the recent Toto lottery win?

detailed.en: Congratulations! The recent Toto lottery results show that the winning number is 1899, and the total prize amount won is RM3,780.00.

question.text: What should I do if I have not received my winnings for the J3 number?
variations: What happens if I don't see my winnings?
How can I check my winnings for J3?

languages.en: What should I do if I have not received my winnings for the J3 number?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya belum menerima kemenangan untuk nombor J3?

detailed.en: If you have not received your winnings for the J3 number, please be patient as the system is processing your winnings. You can check the 'Reports' section between 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM to see the credit. If you still do not see anything, try logging out and logging back in. If the issue persists, provide further details so I can assist you better.
detailed.ms: Jika anda belum menerima kemenangan untuk nombor J3, sila bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses kemenangan anda. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Laporan' antara 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Jika anda masih tidak melihat apa-apa, cuba log keluar dan log masuk semula. Jika masalah berterusan, berikan butiran lanjut supaya saya dapat bantu anda dengan lebih baik.

question.text: What should I do if my ibox top-up has not been credited after 10 minutes?

languages.en: What should I do if my ibox top-up has not been credited after 10 minutes?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up ibox saya belum dikreditkan selepas 10 minit?

detailed.en: For ibox top-ups, the crediting process usually takes between 3 to 10 minutes. If the funds have not been credited after this period, please check your wallet or send a screenshot of the receipt via live chat. For winnings from Jaguar at 9pm, it will be credited automatically, and you can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM for updates. If there are any other issues, please let me know!
detailed.ms: Untuk top-up ibox, biasanya proses kredit mengambil masa antara 3 hingga 10 minit. Jika selepas tempoh itu dana masih belum dikreditkan, sila semak dompet anda atau hantarkan tangkapan skrin resit melalui live chat. Untuk kemenangan dari Jaguar 9pm, ia akan dikreditkan secara automatik, dan anda boleh menyemak bahagian 'Report' antara jam 10:00 malam hingga 10:30 malam untuk kemas kini. Jika ada masalah lain, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: What should I do if I forgot to include my ID during a deposit?
variations: I forgot to put my ID when depositing.
What happens if I don't include my ID in the transfer?

languages.en: What should I do if I forgot to include my ID during a deposit?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya terlupa untuk memasukkan ID semasa deposit?

detailed.en: If you forgot to include your JOKER ID during the transfer, make sure to upload the full receipt to the top-up page in the app. After that, wait for 3-10 minutes for the system to process the transaction. In the future, remember to include your JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' field to speed up the verification process. If you encounter any issues, feel free to contact us via live chat!
detailed.ms: Jika anda terlupa untuk memasukkan ID JOKER semasa transfer, pastikan untuk upload resit penuh ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi. Lepas itu, tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem proses transaksi. Untuk masa depan, ingat untuk masukkan ID JOKER dalam ruangan 'Recipient Reference' supaya proses pengesahan lebih cepat. Jika ada masalah, jangan ragu untuk hubungi kami melalui live chat!

question.text: Is it normal for deposits to take a long time to process?
variations: How long does it usually take for deposits to be completed?
Why is my deposit taking so long?

languages.en: Is it normal for deposits to take a long time to process?
languages.ms: Bos duit masuk ambik masa lama ke

detailed.en: Typically, deposits are completed within 5 to 30 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the money has not yet arrived, please send me a screenshot of the receipt, and I will check it for you. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Biasanya, deposit akan selesai dalam masa 5-30 minit. Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan duit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar screenshot resit kepada saya, dan saya akan semak untuk anda. Terima kasih!

question.text: I have not received my deposit of 500 yet, can you help me with this issue?

languages.en: I have not received my deposit of 500 yet, can you help me with this issue?
languages.ms: Saya belum menerima deposit saya sebanyak 500, bolehkah anda membantu saya dengan isu ini?

detailed.en: I understand, boss! Deposits usually take 5-30 minutes to process. If your 500 has not arrived after 30 minutes, there may be an issue with the system or the bank. Please check your bank transfer logs to ensure it was successful. If it still hasn't arrived, send me a screenshot and I will help resolve it!
detailed.ms: Saya faham, bos! Deposit biasanya mengambil masa 5-30 minit untuk diproses. Jika 500 anda belum tiba selepas 30 minit, mungkin ada masalah dengan sistem atau bank. Sila semak log pemindahan bank anda untuk memastikan ia berjaya. Jika masih tiada, hantar saya tangkapan skrin dan saya akan bantu selesaikan!

question.text: What should I do if I have won a 4D number and want to know about the crediting process?
variations: What happens after winning a 4D number?
How is the winning amount credited to my wallet?

detailed.en: If you have won a 4D number, the system is already in the process of crediting your winnings. The winning amount will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please check the app from time to time to see the updates. If there are any issues, feel free to contact support.
detailed.ms: Jika anda mempunyai nombor 4D yang menang, sistem sudah dalam proses untuk mengkreditkan kemenangan anda. Duit menang akan dimasukkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila semak aplikasi dari semasa ke semasa untuk melihat kemas kini. Jika ada sebarang masalah, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi sokongan.

question.text: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after successfully uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas berjaya memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: After successfully uploading the receipt, please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Selepas berjaya memuat naik resit, sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin akan melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
variations: topup
ATM top up process
how to top up using ATM

languages.en: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top up akaun saya menggunakan ATM?

detailed.en:
To top up using an ATM, follow these steps:

1. Go to any bank ATM that supports interbank transfers.
2. Select the 'Transfer' or 'Money Transfer' menu.
3. Enter our company account number (refer to the top-up page in the app).
4. Enter the top-up amount (Minimum RM10).
5. Confirm the transaction and keep the receipt.
6. Take a picture of the receipt and upload it to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat.
7. The top-up will be processed within 3-10 minutes.

Make sure the receipt is clear and complete to avoid rejection.
If you have any issues or need assistance, reply to us in live chat!
detailed.ms:
Untuk top up menggunakan ATM, ikut langkah-langkah ini:

1. Pergi ke ATM mana-mana bank yang menyokong pemindahan antara bank.
2. Pilih menu 'Transfer' atau 'Pemindahan Wang'.
3. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat kami (rujuk halaman top-up dalam aplikasi).
4. Masukkan amaun top-up (Min RM10).
5. Sahkan transaksi dan simpan resit.
6. Ambil gambar resit dan muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan dalam live chat.
7. Top-up akan diproses dalam 3-10 minit.

Pastikan resit jelas dan lengkap untuk mengelakkan penolakan.
Jika ada masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas kepada kami dalam live chat!

question.text: What should I do after topping up my account in the app?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up my account in the app?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menambah nilai akaun saya dalam aplikasi?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it has not been credited after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas menambah nilai, pastikan untuk memuat naik resit ke halaman tambah nilai dalam aplikasi. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika ia belum masuk selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: Why hasn't the J3 resort payout been processed yet at 9 PM?

languages.en: Why hasn't the J3 resort payout been processed yet at 9 PM?
languages.ms: Kenapa pembayaran resort J3 belum diproses lagi pada jam 9 malam?

detailed.en: The winnings for J3 are usually credited automatically to your wallet. Please wait a moment as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM to see the credit. Thank you for your patience, and may you have a big win!
detailed.ms: Kemenangan untuk J3 biasanya akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila tunggu sebentar, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM hingga 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda, dan semoga anda dapat kemenangan besar!

question.text: What should I do if I forgot my password for logging into my account?
variations: What if I can't remember my password?
How can I reset my password?

languages.en: What should I do if I forgot my password for logging into my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya terlupa kata laluan untuk log masuk ke akaun saya?

detailed.en: If you have forgotten your password, you can click on 'Forgot Password' at the bottom of the login page. Follow the steps provided to reset your password. If you encounter any other issues, just let us know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda terlupa kata laluan, boleh klik pada 'Forgot Password' di bawah halaman log masuk. Ikuti langkah-langkah yang diberikan untuk reset password anda. Jika ada masalah lain, beritahu saja!

question.text: What should I do if my winnings for the 5405 bet in Sandakan have not been credited?
variations: What to do if my winnings are not credited?
How can I check my winnings for the 5405 bet?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings for the 5405 bet in Sandakan have not been credited?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya untuk pertaruhan 5405 di Sandakan belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: If you are talking about winnings that have not been credited, usually winnings for bets like Jaguar at 9 PM will be credited automatically to your wallet. Please check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM for the crediting. If after that time your winnings are still not credited, please contact support directly with a screenshot of your transaction for further verification.
detailed.ms: Jika anda bercakap tentang kemenangan yang belum dikreditkan, biasanya kemenangan untuk pertaruhan seperti Jaguar 9pm akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila semak bahagian 'Laporan' antara 10:00 PM dan 10:30 PM untuk pengkreditan. Jika selepas waktu tersebut kemenangan anda masih belum dikreditkan, sila hubungi sokongan secara langsung dengan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda untuk pengesahan lanjut.

question.text: I am experiencing an issue where my withdrawal has not been processed yet. What should I do?
variations: withdraw belum masuk lagi
my withdrawal hasn't arrived yet

languages.en: I am experiencing an issue where my withdrawal has not been processed yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya mengalami masalah di mana pengeluaran saya belum diproses lagi. Apa yang harus saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If your withdrawal has not been processed for more than 30 minutes, please check the transaction in the app first. If it is still not there, please send the transaction details to live chat support for immediate checking. We will assist you to ensure everything runs smoothly for you. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika pengeluaran anda sudah lebih dari 30 minit tetapi belum masuk, sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu. Jika masih tiada, sila hantarkan butiran transaksi kepada sokongan live chat untuk pemeriksaan segera. Kami akan bantu untuk memastikan semuanya berjalan lancar untuk anda. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: Is the system slow in processing updates, and is there a delay in transactions?
variations: Is there a delay in the system updates?
Why is the system slow in processing?

languages.en: Is the system slow in processing updates, and is there a delay in transactions?
languages.ms: Adakah sistem lambat dalam memproses kemas kini, dan adakah terdapat kelewatan dalam transaksi?

detailed.en: If your top-up is delayed, the system usually takes 3-10 minutes to process. If it still hasn't appeared after that period, ensure you are using the correct method such as ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX). For FPX, if it takes more than 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of your transaction through live chat for further verification. Additionally, if you have a winning 4D number, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little longer today. The winnings will automatically be credited to your wallet, so please check the app from time to time.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda lambat, sistem biasanya memerlukan masa 3-10 minit untuk memproses. Jika selepas tempoh itu masih belum muncul, pastikan anda menggunakan kaedah yang betul seperti ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Pembayaran Pantas (FPX). Untuk FPX, jika lebih dari 10 minit, sila hantar tangkapan skrin transaksi anda melalui live chat untuk pengesahan lanjut. Selain itu, jika anda mempunyai nombor 4D yang menang, mohon bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses dan mungkin mengambil sedikit masa hari ini. Duit kemenangan akan secara automatik dimasukkan ke dalam dompet anda, jadi sila semak aplikasi dari semasa ke semasa.

question.text: Saya ingin tahu tentang proses pengesahan transaksi selepas membuat bank-in. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika transaksi saya tidak muncul?
variations: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika transaksi saya tidak muncul?
Bagaimana cara untuk memastikan transaksi bank-in saya disahkan?

languages.ms: Saya ingin tahu tentang proses pengesahan transaksi selepas membuat bank-in. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika transaksi saya tidak muncul?

detailed.en: To verify your transaction after making a bank-in, please upload your bank-in slip through the WALLET â†’ TOPUP section. The process will take about 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the transaction still hasn't appeared, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.

question.text: What should I do after uploading the top-up receipt of RM200 in the application?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the top-up receipt of RM200 in the application?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit top-up RM200 dalam aplikasi?

detailed.en: After uploading the top-up receipt of RM200, make sure it is done on the top-up page in the application. Wait for 3â€“10 minutes for confirmation; if the funds have not yet been credited, please send the receipt via live chat.
detailed.ms: Selepas memuat naik resit top-up RM200, pastikan ia dilakukan di halaman top-up dalam aplikasi. Tunggu 3â€“10 minit untuk pengesahan; jika dana masih belum masuk, sila hantar resit melalui live chat.

question.text: What should I do after winning in the J3 game and when will my winnings be credited to my wallet?
variations: win xmasuk wallet lg j3 9pm

languages.en: What should I do after winning in the J3 game and when will my winnings be credited to my wallet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menang dalam permainan J3 dan bila kemenangan saya akan dikreditkan ke dalam wallet saya?

detailed.en: Congratulations on winning J3! Your winnings for J2/J3 will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please be patient as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM to see the credit. Thank you for your patience, and I hope you have a big win!
detailed.ms: Tahniah kerana menang J3! Kemenangan anda untuk J2/J3 akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam wallet anda. Sila bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh menyemak bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda, dan semoga anda mendapat kemenangan besar!

question.text: What should I do if my transaction status is still pending?
variations: pending lagi
status tunjuk PENDING

languages.en: What should I do if my transaction status is still pending?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status transaksi saya masih pending?

detailed.en: If your transaction status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the status is still pending, you can contact live chat for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status transaksi anda menunjukkan PENDING, itu bermakna sistem sedang memproses. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih pending, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if my betting winnings have not been credited to my wallet?
variations: What happens if my winnings don't show up?
How long does it take for betting winnings to be credited?

detailed.en: Hi boss, the winnings from your football bet will be credited to your wallet automatically within 24 hours on the same day. Please be patient as the system is processing. If it still hasn't been credited after 24 hours, you can contact us via live chat for verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Hi boss, kemenangan bet bola akan masuk ke wallet secara automatik dalam masa 24 jam pada hari yang sama. Mohon bersabar ya boss, sistem sedang proses. Kalau masih belum masuk selepas 24 jam, boleh roger kami di live chat untuk semakan. Terima kasih atas kesabaran boss!

question.text: What are the winnings and congratulations for the recent game?
variations: Can you tell me about the winnings?
What did I win in the game?
How much did I win?

languages.en: What are the winnings and congratulations for the recent game?
languages.ms: Apakah kemenangan dan ucapan tahniah untuk permainan terbaru?

detailed.en: Congratulations! You won RM8,300.00 in the recent game. Enjoy your winnings!
detailed.ms: Tahniah! Anda telah memenangi RM8,300.00 dalam permainan terbaru. Nikmati kemenangan anda!

question.text: What should I do if my prize winnings are not credited yet?
variations: Why hasn't my prize been credited?
What is the delay in my winnings?

languages.en: What should I do if my prize winnings are not credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan hadiah saya belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: If you have won a prize from Magic Box 4D, it should be automatically credited to your special rewards. If there is a delay, please specify whether you won from 4D, balls, or another game so I can assist you further.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah memenangi hadiah dari Magic Box 4D, ia sepatutnya dikreditkan secara automatik kepada ganjaran khas anda. Jika terdapat kelewatan, sila nyatakan sama ada anda menang dari 4D, bola, atau permainan lain supaya saya boleh membantu anda lebih lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my deposit of RM15 has not been credited yet?
variations: Why hasn't my deposit of RM15 shown up?
What are the steps to take if my RM15 deposit is missing?

languages.en: What should I do if my deposit of RM15 has not been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika deposit RM15 saya belum masuk?

detailed.en: If your deposit of RM15 has not been credited yet, please wait for about 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, deposits are credited within 1-10 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the amount is still not credited, please send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for further verification.
detailed.ms: Jika deposit RM15 anda belum masuk, sila tunggu sekitar 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, deposit akan masuk dalam 1-10 minit. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan jumlah tersebut masih belum masuk, sila hantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk semakan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited after uploading the receipt?
variations: Kredit xmasuk lg
Tlg tgk jp

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum dikreditkan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: If you have uploaded the receipt for the top-up and it has not been credited, please wait for 3-10 minutes for confirmation. If after that it is still not credited, please send the receipt via live chat for further assistance. If you are trying to top-up using Touch 'n Go (TNG) and it is unsuccessful, here are some steps you can try: Ensure you are using the correct method: If using Fast Payment (FPX), make sure to select TNG eWallet in the payment section and wait 1-3 minutes for the system to automatically confirm the transaction. If after 3 minutes it is still not credited, send the FPX transaction receipt to live chat for verification. If using DuitNow Transfer via TNG, ensure you select DuitNow to the bank account number, not a regular eWallet transfer. Manually upload the transaction receipt to the top-up page in the app and wait 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm. If there are still issues, try changing your internet connection (WiFi/Data), check if TNG is under maintenance, or try other methods like ATM/Transfer. If it still does not work, reply to us in live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah memuat naik resit untuk top-up dan ia belum dikreditkan, sila tunggu dalam 3-10 minit untuk pengesahan. Jika selepas itu masih tiada, sila hantar resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut. Jika anda cuba top-up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) dan ia tidak berjaya, berikut adalah beberapa langkah yang boleh anda cuba: Pastikan anda menggunakan kaedah yang betul: Jika menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), pastikan anda memilih TNG eWallet dalam bahagian pembayaran dan tunggu 1-3 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi secara automatik. Jika selepas 3 minit masih tiada, hantar resit transaksi FPX ke live chat untuk semakan. Jika menggunakan DuitNow Transfer melalui TNG, pastikan anda memilih DuitNow ke nombor akaun bank, bukan pemindahan eWallet biasa. Muat naik resit transaksi secara manual ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi dan tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika masih ada masalah, cuba tukar rangkaian internet (WiFi/Data), semak jika TNG sedang dalam penyelenggaraan, atau cuba kaedah lain seperti ATM/Transfer. Jika masih tidak berjaya, balas kepada kami di live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: I am wondering why my top-up has not been credited yet. Can you help me check the status?
variations: Why hasn't my top-up been credited?

languages.en: I am wondering why my top-up has not been credited yet. Can you help me check the status?
languages.ms: Saya ingin tahu mengapa top-up saya belum dikreditkan. Bolehkah anda membantu saya menyemak statusnya?

detailed.en: If the top-up has not been credited, please let me know if you used ATM/Transfer or Fast Payment (FPX). I can help check for you. If using ATM/Transfer, ensure the receipt has been uploaded to the top-up page in the app and wait 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm. If using Fast Payment (FPX), it usually gets credited within 1-3 minutes. If it has been more than 3 minutes and it still hasn't been credited, please send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification. If there are any other issues, reply to us in live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up belum masuk, sila beritahu saya sama ada anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer atau Fast Payment (FPX). Saya boleh bantu semak untuk anda. Jika menggunakan ATM/Transfer, pastikan resit telah dimuat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi dan tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), biasanya akan dikreditkan dalam 1-3 minit. Jika lebih dari 3 minit dan masih belum masuk, hantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk semakan. Jika ada masalah lain, balas kepada kami di live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Is the 918KISS platform currently undergoing maintenance, and what should I do if I encounter issues while trying to access it?

languages.en: Is the 918KISS platform currently undergoing maintenance, and what should I do if I encounter issues while trying to access it?
languages.ms: Adakah platform 918KISS sedang dalam penyelenggaraan, dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya menghadapi masalah semasa cuba mengaksesnya?

detailed.en: If the 918KISS platform is undergoing maintenance, you can try using another bank for withdrawals or wait until the maintenance is completed. If the problem persists, please contact our live chat support for further assistance. Additionally, you can try the following steps: 1. Change your internet connection (e.g., switch from Wi-Fi to mobile data or vice versa). 2. Restart your phone and try logging in again. If you still encounter errors, it is likely that 918KISS is undergoing maintenance. Please be patient, as the system will be back to normal after maintenance is completed. If the issue remains, feel free to reach out to us again.
detailed.ms: Jika platform 918KISS sedang dalam penyelenggaraan, anda boleh cuba menggunakan bank lain untuk pengeluaran atau tunggu sehingga penyelenggaraan selesai. Jika masalah berterusan, sila hubungi sokongan live chat kami untuk bantuan lanjut. Selain itu, anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Tukar sambungan internet (contoh: dari Wi-Fi ke data atau sebaliknya). 2. Restart telefon anda dan cuba log masuk semula. Jika anda masih menghadapi ralat, kemungkinan 918KISS sedang dalam penyelenggaraan. Mohon bersabar, kerana sistem akan kembali normal selepas penyelenggaraan selesai. Jika masalah masih berlanjutan, sila hubungi kami semula.

question.text: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
variations: topup
how to top up using ATM

languages.en: How can I top up my account using an ATM?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top up akaun saya menggunakan ATM?

detailed.en: To top up using an ATM, follow these steps: 1. Go to any bank ATM that supports interbank transfers. 2. Select the 'Transfer' or 'Money Transfer' menu. 3. Enter our company account number (refer to the top-up page in the app). 4. Enter the top-up amount (Min RM10). 5. Confirm the transaction and keep the receipt. 6. Take a picture of the receipt and upload it to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat. 7. The top-up will be processed within 3-10 minutes. Ensure the receipt is clear and complete to avoid rejection. If you have any issues or need assistance, reply to us in live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk top up menggunakan ATM, ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Pergi ke ATM mana-mana bank yang menyokong pemindahan antara bank. 2. Pilih menu 'Transfer' atau 'Pemindahan Wang'. 3. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat kami (rujuk halaman top-up dalam aplikasi). 4. Masukkan amaun top-up (Min RM10). 5. Sahkan transaksi dan simpan resit. 6. Ambil gambar resit dan muat naik ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan dalam live chat. 7. Top-up akan diproses dalam 3-10 minit. Pastikan resit jelas dan lengkap untuk mengelakkan penolakan. Jika ada masalah atau perlukan bantuan, balas kepada kami dalam live chat ya.

languages.en: Can I get a refund if I accidentally transferred money?

detailed.en: If you accidentally transferred money, we are sorry, but we cannot process refunds. What you can do is upload the transaction receipt to the top-up page in the app and use those funds for betting. You need to win at least 30% of the capital before you are eligible to withdraw. Once you meet the requirements, you can request a withdrawal as usual. If you have any issues or need assistance, please reply to us in live chat.

Apa yang boleh anda lakukan: Muat naik resit transaksi ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi dan gunakan dana tersebut untuk bertaruh. Anda perlu menang sekurang-kurangnya 30% daripada modal sebelum layak untuk mengeluarkan. Setelah memenuhi syarat, anda boleh meminta pengeluaran seperti biasa. Jika ada sebarang isu atau anda perlukan bantuan, balas kepada kami dalam live chat ya, boss!

detailed.en: If your top-up or winnings are delayed, it usually takes 1-10 minutes to process. languages.en: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been processed yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum diproses?

detailed.en: If your top-up hasn't been processed yet, please ensure that you have uploaded the receipt correctly and wait for about 3-10 minutes. If there is still no update after that, you can contact live chat with your transaction details for further assistance. Don't worry, we will resolve this!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum diproses, sila pastikan anda telah memuat naik resit dengan betul dan tunggu sekitar 3-10 minit. Jika selepas itu masih tiada kemas kini, anda boleh hubungi live chat dengan maklumat transaksi untuk bantuan lanjut. Jangan risau, kita akan selesaikan ini!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up is delayed after making a deposit?
variations: What to do if my top-up is slow?
How long does it take for a top-up to reflect?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up is delayed after making a deposit?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya lambat selepas membuat deposit?

detailed.en: If your top-up is delayed, please let me know if you are using ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX). For ATM/Transfer, ensure you have uploaded the receipt in the top-up section and wait 1-10 minutes. For FPX, the funds should appear within 1-3 minutes. If it is still delayed, please send a full screenshot via live chat for further verification.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda lambat, sila beritahu saya sama ada anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Fast Payment (FPX). Untuk ATM/Transfer, pastikan anda telah muat naik resit di bahagian top-up dan tunggu 1-10 minit. Untuk FPX, dana sepatutnya muncul dalam 1-3 minit. Jika masih lambat, sila hantar tangkapan layar penuh melalui live chat untuk semakan lanjut.

question.text: Why hasn't the J3 credit been processed into my wallet by 9 PM on Christmas?

languages.en: Why hasn't the J3 credit been processed into my wallet by 9 PM on Christmas?
languages.ms: Kenapa kredit J3 belum diproses ke dalam dompet saya pada pukul 9 malam pada Hari Krismas?

detailed.en: The J3 winnings are usually credited automatically to your wallet. Please wait a moment as the system is processing. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM to see the credit. Thank you for your patience, and may you have a big win!
detailed.ms: Kemenangan J3 biasanya akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila tunggu sebentar, sistem sedang memproses. Anda boleh semak di bahagian 'Report' antara 10:00 PM hingga 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda, dan semoga anda dapat kemenangan besar!

question.text: Bolehkah anda memberitahu saya berapa lama duit biasanya mengambil masa untuk masuk?
variations: Lama btol duit nak masuk ni
Berapa lama duit akan masuk?

languages.en: How long does it usually take for the money to arrive?
languages.ms: Bolehkah anda memberitahu saya berapa lama duit biasanya mengambil masa untuk masuk?

detailed.en: I understand, boss! If the money hasn't arrived after 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of the receipt and I will investigate immediately. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Faham, boss! Jika duit belum masuk selepas 10 minit, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit dan saya akan siasat dengan segera. Terima kasih!

question.text: What should I do if I experience delays in the online demo game?

languages.en: What should I do if I experience delays in the online demo game?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya mengalami kelewatan dalam permainan demo dalam talian?

detailed.en: Unfortunately, there is no option to address delays in the demo mode at this time. However, you can start with small bets using real money, with a minimum of RM10, to experience the game without significant risk. If you need anything else, please let me know!
detailed.ms: Malangnya, tiada pilihan untuk menangani kelewatan dalam mod demo pada masa ini. Namun, anda boleh mula dengan pertaruhan kecil menggunakan wang sebenar, dengan minimum RM10, untuk merasai permainan tanpa risiko besar. Jika anda memerlukan apa-apa lagi, sila beritahu saya!

question.text: What time will I receive points if I win?
variations: When will I get my points for winning?
At what time are points credited after a win?

languages.en: What time will I receive points if I win?
languages.ms: Pukul berapa saya akan menerima mata jika saya menang?

detailed.en: For the Jaguar 9pm win, it will usually be credited automatically to your wallet. You can check the 'Report' section between 10:00 PM and 10:30 PM for confirmation. If you are using IBOX, the process may take a little longer. If after that period your winnings are still not credited, please contact live chat with a screenshot of your transaction for further verification. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Untuk kemenangan bet Jaguar 9pm, biasanya ia akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Anda boleh semak bahagian 'Report' antara pukul 10:00 PM hingga 10:30 PM untuk pengesahan. Jika anda menggunakan IBOX, proses mungkin mengambil sedikit masa lebih lama. Jika selepas tempoh itu kemenangan anda masih belum dikreditkan, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin transaksi anda untuk pengesahan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: Why hasn't the J3 result been credited yet?
variations: kenapa result j3 belum ada

languages.en: Why hasn't the J3 result been credited yet?
languages.ms: Kenapa result J3 belum ada?

detailed.en: If your J3 winnings have not been credited, please wait around 10 minutes for the system to process it. If it still does not appear after that, you can contact live chat with your transaction details for further assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan J3 anda belum dikreditkan, sila tunggu sekitar 10 minit untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jika selepas itu masih belum muncul, anda boleh hubungi live chat dengan butiran transaksi anda untuk bantuan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What are the details of the Magic Box prize I have won?

languages.en: What are the details of the Magic Box prize I have won?
languages.ms: Apakah butiran hadiah Magic Box yang telah saya menangi?

detailed.en: Congratulations! You have won the Magic Box. The winning details are as follows: Winning Field: Magnum, Winning Number: 3751, Winning Letter: L, Total Winnings: RM355.00.
detailed.ms: Tahniah! Anda telah memenangi Magic Box. Butiran kemenangan adalah seperti berikut: Padang Menang: Magnum, Nombor Menang: 3751, Huruf Menang: L, Jumlah Kemenangan: RM355.00.

variations: Saya masok fast payment may bank sudha tolak duit tapi bulum masok boss

languages.ms: Saya telah melakukan top-up sebanyak 50 tetapi masih belum masuk ke dalam akaun saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.ms:
Faham, boss! Jika anda menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX) dan duit sudah ditolak tetapi belum masuk, ada beberapa langkah yang boleh anda cuba:

1. **Semak jika bank sedang dalam penyelenggaraan.**

3. **Cuba lagi selepas beberapa minit.**

Jika masih tidak berjaya, sila hantar tangkapan skrin transaksi kepada live chat untuk semakan lanjut. Saya harap ini membantu! ğŸ˜ŠğŸ™

languages.en: What should I do after topping up my account in the app?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. ğŸ˜Š Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it hasn't been processed after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Thank you for your patience!

Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum diproses, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

I can't play

question.text: What should I do if my bank transfer is not credited after a certain period?
variations: What if my bank transfer doesn't show up?
How long does it take for a bank transfer to be credited?
What to do if my transfer is delayed?

languages.en: What should I do if my bank transfer is not credited after a certain period?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pemindahan bank saya tidak dikreditkan selepas tempoh tertentu?

detailed.en: If you have made a transfer and want to know about the confirmation, usually the amount transferred will be received within 1-10 minutes. Please check your wallet to ensure that the amount has been credited. If you still do not see it, please contact our live chat support for further assistance. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah membuat pemindahan dan ingin tahu tentang pengesahan, biasanya jumlah yang dipindahkan akan diterima dalam masa 1-10 minit. Sila semak dompet anda untuk memastikan jumlah tersebut telah dikreditkan. Jika anda masih tidak melihatnya, sila hubungi sokongan live chat kami untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya, boss!

question.text: I am experiencing issues with the top-up process in the Joker game. Can you help me understand why my top-up is delayed?
variations: top up sedut
top up lambat
masalah top up joker

languages.en: I am experiencing issues with the top-up process in the Joker game. Can you help me understand why my top-up is delayed?
languages.ms: Saya mengalami masalah dengan proses top-up dalam permainan Joker. Bolehkah anda membantu saya memahami mengapa top-up saya lambat?

detailed.en: If your top-up is delayed, it usually takes 3-10 minutes. If it takes longer, the system might be busy. Please wait a moment, and if there are still no updates, send a screenshot of your receipt via live chat for immediate review. Don't worry, we will help resolve this issue!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda lambat, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Jika lebih dari itu, mungkin sistem sedang sibuk. Sila tunggu sebentar, dan jika masih tiada kemas kini, hantar tangkapan skrin resit anda melalui live chat untuk semakan segera. Jangan risau, kita akan bantu selesaikan masalah ini!

question.text: What should I do if my withdrawal was rejected and I want to know if the amount will be returned to my wallet?
variations: What happens if my withdrawal is rejected?
Will the rejected amount come back to my wallet?

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pengeluaran saya ditolak dan saya ingin tahu jika jumlah itu akan dikembalikan ke dompet saya?

detailed.en: If your withdrawal is rejected, the amount should automatically return to your wallet. Please check your wallet first. If the amount is not there, try logging out and logging back into the app. If it still doesn't appear, restart your phone or switch your network (WiFi/Data). If it still hasn't returned after checking, please reply to us in the live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika pengeluaran anda ditolak, jumlah tersebut sepatutnya secara automatik kembali ke dalam dompet anda. Semak dompet anda terlebih dahulu, jika ia tidak ada: Log keluar dan log masuk semula ke dalam aplikasi. Jika masih tidak nampak, cuba mulakan semula telefon anda atau tukar rangkaian (WiFi/Data). Jika ia masih belum kembali selepas semakan, balas kepada kami dalam chat langsung untuk bantuan lanjut!

Once submitted, please wait 3â€“10 minutes for the system to verify. If you have any other questions, just let us know, boss! ğŸ”„ğŸ’°âœ¨
detailed.ms: Untuk top-up dengan berjaya, sila ikuti langkah-langkah ini: 1ï¸âƒ£ Lakukan pemindahan tambahan untuk mencapai jumlah minimum RM10. 2ï¸âƒ£ Kemudian muat naik kedua-dua resit transaksi melalui live chat (âŒ Jangan muat naik ke halaman top-up) supaya kami boleh menggabungkan jumlah tersebut dan memproses top-up anda. Setelah dihantar, sila tunggu 3â€“10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang soalan lain, beritahu kami ya, boss! ğŸ”„ğŸ’°âœ¨

question.text: What should I do after winning a jackpot?

languages.en: What should I do after winning a jackpot?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menang jackpot?

detailed.en: Congratulations on your jackpot win! It's a great opportunity to celebrate and consider how to manage your winnings wisely. You might want to consult with a financial advisor to discuss investment options or saving strategies. Enjoy your win and make the most of it!
detailed.ms: Tahniah atas kemenangan jackpot anda! Ini adalah peluang yang baik untuk meraikan dan mempertimbangkan cara untuk menguruskan kemenangan anda dengan bijak. Anda mungkin ingin berunding dengan penasihat kewangan untuk membincangkan pilihan pelaburan atau strategi simpanan. Nikmati kemenangan anda dan manfaatkan sebaiknya!

question.text: What should I do if my withdrawal hasn't been processed yet?
variations: What to do if my withdrawal is not showing up?
How long does it take for a withdrawal to be processed?

languages.en: What should I do if my withdrawal hasn't been processed yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pengeluaran saya belum diproses?

detailed.en: If your withdrawal hasn't been processed yet, please check your bank account. The withdrawal process usually takes 5-30 minutes. If it has been more than 30 minutes and it still hasn't appeared, you can send your transaction details to live chat for immediate checking. Also, check your wallet to see if the credit has been returned. If it still hasn't appeared, send your transaction details to live chat for immediate assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika pengeluaran anda belum diproses, sila semak akaun bank anda. Proses pengeluaran biasanya mengambil masa 5-30 minit. Jika sudah lebih 30 minit dan masih belum muncul, anda boleh menghantar butiran transaksi anda ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Juga, semak dalam wallet anda untuk melihat jika kredit telah dikembalikan. Jika masih belum muncul, hantar butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk bantuan segera.

question.text: I am experiencing issues with my login, as I was able to log in earlier but now I cannot. What should I do?
variations: I was able to log in before, but now I can't.
I had access earlier, but now it's gone.

languages.en: I am experiencing issues with my login, as I was able to log in earlier but now I cannot. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya mengalami masalah dengan log masuk saya, kerana saya dapat log masuk sebelum ini tetapi sekarang saya tidak dapat. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you are experiencing issues logging in, here are some steps you can try: 1. Refresh the page or close and reopen the app. 2. Check your internet connection, whether WiFi or mobile data. 3. Try logging in again with the correct password. If you forgot it, use the 'Forgot Password' option on the login page. If the problem persists, let me know, and we can find another solution!
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah untuk log masuk, mungkin ada beberapa langkah yang boleh dicuba: 1. Segarkan halaman atau tutup dan buka semula aplikasi. 2. Periksa sambungan internet anda, sama ada WiFi atau data mudah alih. 3. Cuba semula dengan kata laluan yang betul. Jika terlupa, gunakan pilihan 'Lupa Kata Laluan' di bawah halaman log masuk. Jika masalah masih berterusan, beritahu saya, dan kita boleh cari jalan penyelesaian lain!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up is delayed?
variations: Why is my top-up taking so long?
How can I check the status of my top-up?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up is delayed?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya lambat?

detailed.en: If your second top-up is delayed, please let me know whether you are using ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) or Fast Payment (FPX). For ATM/Transfer, it usually takes 1-10 minutes after you upload the receipt. For FPX, it should appear at the same time. If it takes longer than that, please send a screenshot of your transaction via live chat for further checking.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up kedua lambat masuk, boleh beritahu saya sama ada anda menggunakan ATM/Transfer (DuitNow) atau Fast Payment (FPX)? Untuk ATM/Transfer, biasanya ia mengambil masa 1-10 minit selepas anda muat naik resit. Untuk FPX, sepatutnya ia muncul dalam masa yang sama. Jika lebih dari itu, sila hantar tangkapan skrin transaksi anda melalui live chat untuk semakan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: What should I do after topping up my account to ensure my transaction is processed correctly?

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas topup akaun saya untuk memastikan transaksi saya diproses dengan betul?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it hasn't been processed after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas topup, pastikan resit sudah diupload ke halaman topup dalam app. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi. Kalau lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up has not been processed yet?
variations: What if my top-up is still not showing?
What to do if my transaction hasn't gone through?
How long should I wait for my top-up to appear?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up has not been processed yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum diproses?

detailed.en: If your top-up has not been processed, please upload your transaction receipt once and wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm. If you upload the same receipt twice, the system may reject the transaction and it will take longer to process. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the top-up still hasn't appeared, please send your transaction receipt to live chat for immediate assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum diproses, sila muat naik resit transaksi anda sekali sahaja dan tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika anda muat naik resit yang sama dua kali, sistem mungkin akan menolak transaksi dan ia akan mengambil masa lebih lama untuk diproses. Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan top-up masih belum muncul, sila hantar resit transaksi anda ke live chat untuk bantuan segera.

question.text: Saya mengalami masalah dengan top-up iBox 2081 yang belum dikreditkan. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
variations: Kenapa top-up iBox saya belum muncul?
Bagaimana cara menyelesaikan masalah top-up iBox?

languages.ms: Saya mengalami masalah dengan top-up iBox 2081 yang belum dikreditkan. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah dengan top-up iBox yang belum dikreditkan, biasanya prosesnya mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Jika selepas itu masih belum muncul, sila semak dompet anda atau hantar tangkapan skrin resit melalui live chat. Kemenangan 4D akan dikreditkan ke wallet JOKER secara automatik. Mohon bersabar ya, sistem sedang memproses.

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: Hi boss, the receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Hai bos, resit sudah berjaya diupload ya. Mohon bos tunggu sebentar untuk sistem proses. Jangan upload resit yang sama lagi ya, nanti sistem akan jadi lambat. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama bos!

question.text: What are the details of the winnings from the Magic Box?

languages.en: What are the details of the winnings from the Magic Box?

detailed.en: Congratulations! You have won the Magic Box. The winning details are as follows: Winning Field: Horse, Winning Number: 6099, Winning Letter: F, Total Winnings: RM355.00.
detailed.ms: Tahniah! Anda telah memenangi Magic Box. Butiran kemenangan adalah seperti berikut: Padang Menang: Kuda, Nombor Menang: 6099, Huruf Menang: F, Jumlah Kemenangan: RM355.00.

question.text: Saya sudah melakukan transfer tetapi duit tidak masuk ke dalam akaun saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
variations: Duit saya sudah ditolak tetapi belum masuk.
Apa yang perlu saya buat jika transfer saya tidak berjaya?

languages.ms: Saya sudah melakukan transfer tetapi duit tidak masuk ke dalam akaun saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If the money has been deducted from your account but has not yet been credited, there may be a technical issue or an error with the transaction. Please wait for about 3-10 minutes. If there is still no credit, send a screenshot of the receipt to live chat for further verification. We hope it gets resolved quickly so you can buy numbers for the 9pm draw!
detailed.ms: Jika duit sudah ditolak dari akaun tetapi belum masuk, mungkin ada masalah teknikal atau kesilapan dengan transaksi. Sila tunggu sekitar 3-10 minit lagi. Jika masih tiada kemasukan, hantar tangkapan skrin resit kepada live chat untuk semakan lanjut. Semoga cepat selesai supaya anda boleh beli nombor untuk draw 9pm!

question.text: What should I do if I accidentally topped up only RM9 instead of the minimum RM10 required?

languages.en: What should I do if I accidentally topped up only RM9 instead of the minimum RM10 required?
languages.ms: Apa perlu buat jika saya terisi 9 ringgit dan bukannya minimum RM10 yang diperlukan?

detailed.en: To proceed with the top-up, you need to transfer an additional RM10 to meet the minimum requirement of RM10. Once you do that, the total will be combined to RM19, and we will process your top-up. Please ensure to send the receipt within 24 hours. Make sure to send both receipts here in the live chat and not upload them in the app.
detailed.ms: Untuk meneruskan pengisian semula, anda perlu memindahkan tambahan RM10 untuk memenuhi keperluan minimum RM10. Setelah anda melakukannya, jumlah akan digabungkan menjadi RM19, dan kami akan memproses pengisian semula anda. Sila pastikan untuk menghantar resit dalam tempoh 24 jam. Pastikan untuk menghantar kedua-dua resit di sini dalam live chat dan bukan memuat naiknya dalam aplikasi.

question.text: What should I do if my payment has been made but the funds have not been credited to my account?
variations: What happens if my payment is not reflected?
How long does it take for the funds to be credited after payment?

languages.en: What should I do if my payment has been made but the funds have not been credited to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pembayaran saya telah dibuat tetapi dana belum dikreditkan ke akaun saya?

detailed.en: If you have made the payment but the funds have not been credited, please wait for about 3-10 minutes. If the funds still do not appear after that, please contact live chat for immediate assistance. I hope everything will be resolved quickly!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah bayar tetapi dana belum dikredit, sila tunggu sekitar 3-10 minit. Jika masih belum masuk selepas itu, sila hubungi live chat untuk bantuan segera. Saya harap semuanya akan selesai dengan cepat!

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum dikreditkan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: If your top-up hasn't been credited, please wait between 3 to 10 minutes after uploading the receipt. If the funds still do not appear, contact live chat support with your complete receipt for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum masuk, sila tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit selepas memuat naik resit. Jika dana masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi sokongan live chat dengan resit lengkap anda untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: Why hasn't my winning amount been updated in my account?

languages.en: Why hasn't my winning amount been updated in my account?
languages.ms: Kenapa kemenangan saya belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: The winnings are usually credited automatically within 5 to 30 minutes due to high transaction volumes. If your winnings do not appear within the standard time, please be patient or contact our live chat support for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Kemenangan biasanya akan dikreditkan secara automatik dalam masa 5 hingga 30 minit disebabkan oleh jumlah transaksi yang tinggi. Jika kemenangan anda tidak muncul dalam masa yang standard, sila bersabar atau hubungi sokongan live chat kami untuk bantuan lanjut.
