detailed.en: To fix the issue of games not opening, try the following steps: 1. Close and reopen the game application. 2. Log out and log back into the Joker app, then try again. 3. Change your internet connection (try WiFi or mobile data). 4. Check if the game is under maintenance â€“ if so, wait until it is completed. 5. Try reinstalling the game using the correct link. If it still doesn't open, send a screenshot of the error to live chat so we can assist further.
detailed.ms: Untuk memperbaiki masalah game yang tidak boleh dibuka, cuba langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Tutup dan buka semula aplikasi game. 2. Semak jika game sedang dalam penyelenggaraan â€“ jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai. 5. Cuba pasang semula game menggunakan pautan yang betul. Jika masih tidak boleh dibuka, hantar tangkapan layar kesilapan ke live chat supaya kami dapat membantu lebih lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my winnings from the 4D lottery have not been credited to my wallet yet?

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings from the 4D lottery have not been credited to my wallet yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya dari loteri 4D belum dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: If you have won the 4D lottery, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little time today. The winnings will be credited to your wallet automatically. Please check the app from time to time. If it has been more than 30 minutes and the winnings have still not been credited, you can contact us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.
detailed.ms: Jika anda menang loteri 4D, mohon bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses dan mungkin mengambil sedikit masa hari ini. Duit kemenangan akan dikreditkan ke dalam dompet anda secara automatik. Sila semak aplikasi dari semasa ke semasa. Jika lebih dari 30 minit dan duit kemenangan masih belum dikreditkan, anda boleh hubungi kami semula dengan tangkapan layar resit dan keputusan.

languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas topup menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX)?

detailed.en: After topping up using Fast Payment (FPX), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, the funds will be credited within 1-10 minutes. If the funds do not appear after 10 minutes, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Selepas topup menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), sila tunggu selama 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, dana akan dikreditkan dalam masa 1-10 minit. Jika dana tidak muncul selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pengesahan.

languages.ms: Apakah peraturan mengenai deposit, bonus, dan pemindahan antara ID berkaitan dengan pertaruhan?

question.text: What does '2N' mean in the context of betting, particularly in 4D games?
variations: What is the meaning of '2N' in betting?
Can you explain '2N' in 4D betting?

languages.en: What does '2N' mean in the context of betting, particularly in 4D games?
languages.ms: Apa maksud '2N' dalam konteks pertaruhan, terutamanya dalam permainan 4D?

detailed.en: '2N' refers to a betting category that includes all prizes for the last two digits of a 4D number. For example, if the winning 4D number is 1234, '2N' will consider the last two digits, which are 34. This means all combinations ending with 34 will win.
detailed.ms: '2N' merujuk kepada kategori pertaruhan yang meliputi semua hadiah untuk dua digit terakhir dari nombor 4D. Jadi, jika nombor 4D yang menang adalah 1234, maka '2N' akan mengambil kira dua digit terakhir, iaitu 34. Ini bermakna semua kombinasi yang berakhir dengan 34 akan menang.

question.text: What should I do if I transferred credit to the wrong ID and haven't received my money back?
variations: What can I do if my credit transfer to a friend went wrong?
How can I recover my funds after sending them to the wrong account?

languages.en: What should I do if I transferred credit to the wrong ID and haven't received my money back?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya telah memindahkan kredit kepada ID yang salah dan belum menerima wang saya kembali?

detailed.en: If you have transferred credit to the wrong ID, I apologize, but the system cannot automatically return it. Please provide me with the wrong JOKER ID you transferred to and the amount of credit involved. We will try to contact the owner of that ID and ask them to return the credit in the same way (Credit Share). However, there is no guarantee that the credit can be returned, as it depends on the owner of the receiving ID. For future transfers, please ensure that the ID entered is correct before pressing send. If you have any other questions, just reply in the live chat!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah transfer kredit kepada ID yang salah, minta maaf ya, sistem tidak boleh mengembalikan secara automatik. Sila berikan saya JOKER ID yang anda transfer secara salah dan jumlah kredit yang terlibat. Kami akan cuba hubungi pemilik ID tersebut dan minta mereka untuk mengembalikan kredit dengan cara yang sama (Credit Share). Namun, tiada jaminan kredit boleh dikembalikan, ia bergantung kepada pemilik ID yang menerima. Untuk masa akan datang, pastikan ID yang dimasukkan adalah betul sebelum tekan hantar ya! Jika ada soalan lain, balas saja di live chat ya!

variations: saya withdraw duit

languages.en: How can I withdraw money from my account and what should I do if the withdrawal doesn't appear after some time?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh mengeluarkan duit dari akaun saya dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pengeluaran tidak muncul selepas beberapa waktu?

detailed.en: To withdraw money from your account, follow these steps in the app: 1. Click the 'Wallet' icon (at the bottom center of the screen). 2. Select 'Withdraw'. 3. Ensure the selected bank has a 'Primary' tag. 4. Enter the amount you wish to withdraw (Min RM10). 5. Click 'Submit' to send the withdrawal request. 6. Wait 5-30 minutes for the process to complete. If the withdrawal has not appeared after 10 minutes, please send a screenshot of the withdrawal receipt to us for immediate investigation. If it has been more than 30 minutes, check your bank account and if it still hasn't appeared, send the transaction details to live chat for immediate checking.
detailed.ms: Untuk mengeluarkan duit dari akaun anda, ikut langkah-langkah ini dalam aplikasi: 1. Klik ikon 'Wallet' (di tengah bawah skrin). 2. Pilih 'Withdraw'. 3. Pastikan bank yang dipilih mempunyai tanda 'Primary'. 4. Masukkan jumlah yang ingin dikeluarkan (Min RM10). 5. Klik 'Submit' untuk menghantar permohonan pengeluaran. 6. Tunggu 5-30 minit untuk proses selesai. Jika pengeluaran duit sudah lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum masuk, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit pengeluaran kepada kami. Kami akan siasat dengan segera.

Selain itu, jika ada nombor 4D kena, mohon sabar ya â€” sistem sedang proses dan mungkin ambil masa sikit hari ni. Duit menang akan masuk ke wallet boss secara automatik, sila semak dari semasa ke semasa dalam app.

question.text: Saya sudah topup melalui Maybank tetapi nombor akaun sudah ditukar. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?
variations: Saya sudah topup tetapi tidak masuk.
Saya sudah bank in tetapi masih belum masuk.
Bagaimana jika saya sudah topup tetapi tidak menerima kredit?

languages.en: I have topped up through Maybank but the account number has changed. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya sudah topup melalui Maybank tetapi nombor akaun sudah ditukar. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: If you have topped up through Maybank but the account number has changed, there may be an issue with the transaction. Please check your transaction details and ensure that you have entered the correct information. If there are discrepancies, you need to report this issue immediately through live chat with the complete transaction receipt. If you accidentally transferred funds to the wrong account, those funds may not be recoverable. If there's anything else I can assist you with, just let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah top-up melalui Maybank tetapi nombor akaun sudah ditukar, mungkin ada masalah dengan transaksi tersebut. Sila semak butiran transaksi anda dan pastikan bahawa anda telah memasukkan maklumat yang betul. Jika ada ketidaksesuaian, anda perlu melaporkan isu ini segera melalui live chat dengan resit transaksi yang lengkap. Jika anda secara tidak sengaja memindahkan dana ke akaun yang salah, dana tersebut mungkin tidak dapat dipulihkan.

question.text: What should I do to resend the receipt for the last claim to the Top-Up section?

languages.en: What should I do to resend the receipt for the last claim to the Top-Up section?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan untuk menghantar semula resit untuk tuntutan terakhir ke bahagian Top-Up?

detailed.en: Please resend the receipt to the Top-Up section as this is the final claim. Make sure to check the list of bank accounts in the app before making the transfer to avoid any mistakes. Thank you for your cooperation!
detailed.ms: Sila hantar semula resit ke bahagian Top-Up kerana ini adalah tuntutan terakhir. Mohon semak senarai akaun bank dalam aplikasi sebelum membuat pemindahan untuk mengelakkan sebarang kesilapan. Terima kasih atas kerjasama anda!

question.text: What should I do when I feel unlucky in a game?

languages.en: What should I do when I feel unlucky in a game?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan apabila saya merasa tidak bernasib baik dalam permainan?

detailed.en: I understand how you feel. If today hasn't brought you luck, remember that tomorrow is still a chance! Keep enjoying the game, as luck can come at any time. I wish you a lot of luck and a big jackpot in the next draw!
detailed.ms: Saya faham perasaan anda. Jika hari ini belum membawa rezeki, ingatlah bahawa esok masih ada peluang! Teruskan menikmati permainan, kerana nasib boleh datang bila-bila masa. Saya doakan anda banyak nasib dan jackpot besar dalam cabutan seterusnya!

question.text: What should I do if I made a mistake in my top-up transaction?
variations: I made a mistake in my top-up, what now?
How do I correct a wrong top-up amount?

languages.en: What should I do if I made a mistake in my top-up transaction?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya membuat kesilapan dalam transaksi top-up saya?

detailed.en: If you have entered the wrong amount in your top-up, please resend the transaction by uploading the correct receipt with the accurate amount. The system will process your updated top-up within 3-10 minutes. If the credit still does not appear, please contact live chat with a screenshot of your receipt for further assistance. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah memasukkan amaun yang salah dalam top-up, sila hantar semula transaksi dengan memuat naik resit yang betul dengan amaun yang tepat. Sistem akan memproses top-up anda yang dikemas kini dalam masa 3-10 minit. Jika kredit masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan skrin resit anda untuk bantuan lanjut. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: What should I do if my credit has not been approved after a top-up?
variations: credit saya x aprove
my credit is not approved

languages.en: What should I do if my credit has not been approved after a top-up?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kredit saya tidak diluluskan selepas top-up?

detailed.en: If your top-up has not been credited, make sure you have uploaded the transaction receipt in the top-up section of the app. Wait for 3-10 minutes for the system to process. If it is still not credited after 10 minutes, please send the transaction receipt via live chat for immediate assistance. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum dikreditkan, pastikan anda telah memuat naik resit transaksi di bahagian top-up dalam aplikasi. Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem memproses. Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantar resit transaksi melalui live chat untuk bantuan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up at Kabali Smart has not been credited yet?
variations: How can I check the status of my top-up?
What steps should I take if my top-up is delayed?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up at Kabali Smart has not been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya di Kabali Smart belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: If you have topped up and the funds have not been credited, please ensure you have uploaded the receipt correctly. Wait for 3-10 minutes after uploading. If the funds still do not appear, please contact live chat support with your complete receipt for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah top-up dan dana belum dikreditkan, sila pastikan anda telah memuat naik resit dengan betul. Tunggu 3-10 minit selepas memuat naik. Jika dana masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi sokongan live chat dengan resit lengkap anda untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What are the details of the recent Toto lottery win?

languages.en: What are the details of the recent Toto lottery win?

detailed.en: Congratulations! The recent Toto lottery win was for the STRIKE category with the winning number 5787, resulting in a prize of RM6,500.00.

question.text: What should I do with my old bank account that I no longer use for transactions?

languages.en: What should I do with my old bank account that I no longer use for transactions?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan dengan akaun bank lama saya yang tidak lagi saya gunakan untuk transaksi?

detailed.en: Please follow the bank account listed in your Joker app for transfers. This is the last claim. Any future deposits into this old account will be considered void. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Sila ikut bank acc yang ada dalam joker apps anda untuk transfer. Ini adalah tuntutan terakhir. Sebarang deposit masa depan ke dalam akaun lama ini akan dianggap tidak sah. Terima kasih!

question.text: Is the receipt uploaded by the user the correct one for the company account?

languages.en: Is the receipt uploaded by the user the correct one for the company account?
languages.ms: Adakah resit yang dimuat naik oleh pengguna adalah yang betul untuk akaun syarikat?

detailed.en: The receipt uploaded is not for our company account. Please check if you have uploaded the correct receipt.
detailed.ms: Resit yang dimuat naik bukan untuk akaun syarikat kami. Sila semak jika anda telah memuat naik resit yang betul.

question.text: I made a mistake in my submission amount, can you help me correct it?
variations: I submitted the wrong amount, how can I fix it?
I need to correct my submission amount.

languages.en: I made a mistake in my submission amount, can you help me correct it?
languages.ms: Saya telah membuat kesilapan dalam jumlah pengesahan saya, bolehkah anda membantu saya membetulkannya?

detailed.en: You submitted RM104 by mistake. Please correct it to RM10 and submit again. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Anda telah menghantar RM104 secara tidak sengaja. Sila betulkannya kepada RM10 dan hantar semula. Terima kasih!

question.text: How can I share credit and what should I do if I shared it with the wrong ID?
variations: Where can I share credit?
What to do if I shared credit incorrectly?

languages.en: How can I share credit and what should I do if I shared it with the wrong ID?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh berkongsi kredit dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya berkongsi dengan ID yang salah?

detailed.en: If you have shared credit with the wrong ID, unfortunately, the system cannot automatically return it. Please provide the incorrect JOKER ID you shared and the amount of credit involved. We will try to contact the owner of that ID and ask them to return the credit in the same way (Credit Share). However, there is no guarantee that the credit can be returned, as it depends on the owner of the ID who received it. In the future, please ensure that the ID entered is correct before pressing the send button.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah berkongsi kredit dengan ID yang salah, maaf ya, sistem tidak dapat mengembalikan secara automatik. Sila berikan JOKER ID yang anda kongsi secara salah dan jumlah kredit yang terlibat. Kami akan cuba menghubungi pemilik ID tersebut dan meminta mereka untuk mengembalikan kredit dengan cara yang sama (Credit Share). Namun, tiada jaminan bahawa kredit dapat dikembalikan, ia bergantung kepada pemilik ID yang menerimanya. Lain kali, pastikan ID yang dimasukkan adalah betul sebelum menekan butang hantar ya!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up is delayed after banking in?
variations: What to do if my top-up is slow?
How long does it take for the top-up to reflect?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up is delayed after banking in?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya lambat selepas bank in?

detailed.en: If you have banked in RM33 and the funds do not appear within 1-10 minutes, please upload your bank-in receipt in the top-up section and wait for further verification. If there are any issues, let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah bank in RM33 dan dana tidak muncul dalam 1-10 minit, sila muat naik resit bank in anda di bahagian top-up dan tunggu untuk semakan lanjut. Jika ada apa-apa masalah, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: Bagaimana cara untuk menukar akaun bank dalam aplikasi dan memastikan semua maklumat betul?
variations: Mcm mana nak tukar akaun bank?
Apa langkah-langkah untuk tukar akaun bank dalam aplikasi?

languages.en: How to change bank account in the app and ensure all information is correct?
languages.ms: Bagaimana cara untuk menukar akaun bank dalam aplikasi dan memastikan semua maklumat betul?

detailed.en: To change your bank account in the app, follow these steps: 1. Go to the 'Wallet' section in the app. 2. Select 'Withdrawal'. 3. Then, choose 'Add Account' to enter your new bank details. Make sure the bank account name matches the registered profile. If you encounter any issues, feel free to contact our live chat support for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk menukar akaun bank dalam aplikasi, anda boleh ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Pergi ke bahagian 'Dompet' dalam aplikasi. 2. Pilih 'Pengeluaran'. 3. Kemudian, pilih 'Tambah Akaun' untuk masukkan butiran bank baru anda. Pastikan nama akaun bank yang anda masukkan sepadan dengan profil yang didaftarkan. Jika ada masalah, jangan ragu untuk hubungi sokongan live chat kami untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if I mistakenly transferred money to the wrong bank account?
variations: What happens if I send money to the wrong account?
How can I resolve a mistaken bank transfer?

languages.en: What should I do if I mistakenly transferred money to the wrong bank account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tersilap memindahkan wang ke akaun bank yang salah?

detailed.en: If you have transferred money to the wrong account and did not receive a receipt, please upload a screenshot or proof of the transaction in the top-up section of the app. The process usually takes 3-10 minutes; if it takes longer, please contact live chat with a full screenshot for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda sudah transfer menggunakan ATM tetapi slip tidak keluar, sila muat naik tangkapan layar atau bukti transaksi di bahagian top-up dalam aplikasi. Proses biasanya mengambil masa 3-10 minit; jika lebih dari itu, sila hubungi live chat dengan tangkapan layar penuh untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited to my account?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up hasn't been credited to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya?

detailed.en: Hi boss, please follow the bank list in the app for the transfer. Make sure to use the account displayed on the top-up page to ensure the transaction goes smoothly. Do not 'Favourite' our bank account as the account number may change from time to time. If you have any other questions, feel free to contact us via live chat!
detailed.ms: Hai bos, sila ikut senarai bank dalam aplikasi untuk pemindahan. Pastikan anda menggunakan akaun yang tertera pada halaman top-up untuk memastikan transaksi berjalan lancar. Jangan 'Favourite' akaun bank kami kerana nombor akaun mungkin akan berubah dari semasa ke semasa. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang pertanyaan lain, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat!

question.text: Bagaimana cara untuk melakukan transfer menggunakan aplikasi Kabali?
variations: MCM mn bos
yg ni MCM mn bos

languages.ms: Bagaimana cara untuk melakukan transfer menggunakan aplikasi Kabali?

Hi boss, sila ikut senarai bank dalam app untuk buat transfer ya. ğŸ˜ŠğŸ”¥

question.text: What information do I need to provide for a refund to the account owner Muhammad Amirul Bin Kamarul Baharain?

languages.en: What information do I need to provide for a refund to the account owner Muhammad Amirul Bin Kamarul Baharain?
languages.ms: Apakah maklumat yang perlu saya berikan untuk proses refund kepada pemilik akaun Muhammad Amirul Bin Kamarul Baharain?

detailed.en: To process the refund to the account owner Muhammad Amirul Bin Kamarul Baharain, please ensure that all the provided information is accurate. The required details are: Bank Name: CIMB BANK, Account Number: 7650697537, Owner Name: Muhammad Amirul Bin Kamarul Baharain. If all this information is correct, we will proceed with the refund.
detailed.ms: Untuk proses refund kepada pemilik akaun Muhammad Amirul Bin Kamarul Baharain, sila pastikan semua maklumat yang diberikan adalah tepat. Nama Bank: CIMB BANK, Nombor Akaun: 7650697537, Nama Pemilik: Muhammad Amirul Bin Kamarul Baharain. Jika semua maklumat ini betul, kami akan uruskan refund tersebut.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up money has not been credited after uploading the receipt?
variations: What to do if the money hasn't arrived?
How long does it take for the top-up to reflect?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up money has not been credited after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika duit top-up saya belum dikreditkan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: If your top-up has not been credited, please wait between 3 to 10 minutes after uploading the receipt. If the money still does not appear, please contact live chat support with your complete receipt. Good luck!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum dikreditkan, sila tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit selepas memuat naik resit. Jika duit masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi sokongan live chat dengan resit lengkap anda. Semoga berjaya!

question.text: What should I do if I cannot open the 918Kiss application?
variations: I can't open 918Kiss
How to fix 918Kiss not opening

languages.en: What should I do if I cannot open the 918Kiss application?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tidak dapat membuka aplikasi 918Kiss?

detailed.en:
To fix the issue of 918Kiss not opening, try the following steps:
1. Close and reopen the 918Kiss application.
2. Log out and log back into the Joker App, then re-enter your ID and Password.
3. Try switching your internet connection (from WiFi to mobile data or vice versa).
4. Check if the game is under maintenance â€“ if so, wait until it is completed.
5. Try reinstalling the game using the correct download links:
   - Download 918Kiss: https://m-918kiss.com
   - http://b1.918kiss.com
If the problem persists, please respond to us in live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms:
Untuk memperbaiki masalah 918Kiss tidak boleh dibuka, cuba langkah-langkah berikut:
1. Tutup dan buka semula aplikasi 918Kiss.
2. Log keluar dan log masuk semula ke dalam Aplikasi Joker, kemudian salin semula ID dan Kata Laluan.
3. Cuba tukar sambungan internet (WiFi ke data atau sebaliknya).
4. Semak jika permainan sedang dalam penyelenggaraan â€“ jika ya, tunggu sehingga selesai.
5. Cuba pasang semula permainan menggunakan pautan yang betul ini:
   - Muat Turun 918Kiss: https://m-918kiss.com
   - http://b1.918kiss.com
Jika masalah berterusan, balas kepada kami dalam live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: How can I play Perdana using the Tesla application?

languages.en: How can I play Perdana using the Tesla application?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh bermain Perdana menggunakan aplikasi Tesla?

detailed.en: To play Perdana, you can use the Tesla application. You can download the Tesla app from the provided link. In the Tesla app, you can place bets on 4D for J2, J3, Perdana, and Lucky. You can also check payments and results for this platform. If you have any issues or need assistance, feel free to reply to us in the live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk bermain Perdana, anda boleh menggunakan aplikasi Tesla. Anda boleh memuat turun aplikasi Tesla dari pautan yang disediakan. Dalam aplikasi Tesla, anda boleh membuat pertaruhan 4D untuk J2, J3, Perdana, dan Lucky. Anda juga boleh menyemak pembayaran dan keputusan untuk platform ini. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang masalah atau memerlukan bantuan, sila balas kepada kami dalam chat langsung.

question.text: What should I do after topping up my account in the app?

languages.en: What should I do after topping up my account in the app?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas menambah nilai akaun saya dalam aplikasi?

detailed.en: After topping up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. ğŸ˜Š Wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it hasn't been credited after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Selepas menambah nilai, pastikan untuk memuat naik resit ke halaman tambah nilai dalam aplikasi. ğŸ˜Š Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika ia belum masuk selepas 10 minit, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do if my child is sick and I am worried about our financial situation?

languages.en: What should I do if my child is sick and I am worried about our financial situation?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika anak saya sakit dan saya bimbang tentang keadaan kewangan kami?

detailed.en: I understand your concerns! I hope your child gets well soon. If there's anything I can assist you with, just let me know!
detailed.ms: Saya faham kebimbangan anda! Saya harap anak anda cepat sembuh. Jika ada yang boleh saya bantu, beritahu saja, ya!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up using Fast Payment is delayed?
variations: Why is my top-up taking so long?
What to do if my top-up hasn't been credited yet?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up using Fast Payment is delayed?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya menggunakan Fast Payment lambat?

detailed.en: If you have used Fast Payment and your top-up is still delayed, there may be a slight delay in the system. Typically, it should be credited within 1-10 minutes. If it has been more than that, I recommend sending a screenshot of the transaction through live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda menggunakan Fast Payment dan masih lambat, mungkin ada sedikit kelewatan dalam sistem. Biasanya, ia sepatutnya masuk dalam 1-10 minit. Jika sudah lebih dari itu, saya sarankan anda hantar screenshot transaksi melalui live chat untuk kami semak lebih lanjut.

question.text: What steps should I follow to obtain a complete receipt from Maybank?

languages.en: What steps should I follow to obtain a complete receipt from Maybank?
languages.ms: Langkah-langkah apa yang perlu saya ikuti untuk mendapatkan resit lengkap dari Maybank?

detailed.en: To obtain a complete receipt from Maybank, please follow these steps: 1. Tap on 'Accounts'. 2. Select your bank account. 3. Tap on 'View Receipts'. 4. Click the download button as shown in the image. Ensure that the receipt you send is complete as per the example provided. If you encounter any issues, please contact us via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk mendapatkan resit lengkap dari Maybank, sila ikut langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Tekan 'Accounts'. 2. Pilih akaun bank anda. 3. Tekan 'View Receipts'. 4. Tekan butang muat turun seperti yang ditunjukkan dalam gambar. Pastikan resit yang anda hantar lengkap seperti contoh yang diberikan. Jika anda menghadapi sebarang masalah, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if I am unable to log in to my account?
variations: Knp lmbt masuk

languages.en: What should I do if I am unable to log in to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tidak dapat log masuk ke akaun saya?

detailed.en: If you are experiencing issues logging in, ensure that your login information is correct. Try restarting your device and logging in again. If the problem persists, check your internet connection and try clearing the app cache or using a different browser. If the issue still exists, please contact our live chat support for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah untuk log masuk, pastikan maklumat log masuk anda betul. Cuba mulakan semula peranti anda dan log masuk semula. Jika masalah berterusan, semak sambungan internet anda dan cuba kosongkan cache aplikasi atau gunakan pelayar yang berbeza. Jika masalah masih ada, sila hubungi sokongan sembang langsung kami untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What does it mean when the status shows PENDING in the system?

languages.en: What does it mean when the status shows PENDING in the system?
languages.ms: Apa maksudnya apabila status menunjukkan PENDING dalam sistem?

detailed.en: When the status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing your request. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it takes more than 10 minutes, you can contact live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Apabila status menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memproses permintaan anda. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem menyelesaikan proses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika ia mengambil masa lebih dari 10 minit, anda boleh menghubungi live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: I have made a withdrawal of RM40, but it has not been credited to my account yet. What should I do?
variations: Why hasn't my RM40 withdrawal been credited yet?
What to do if my withdrawal is delayed?

languages.en: I have made a withdrawal of RM40, but it has not been credited to my account yet. What should I do?
languages.ms: Saya telah membuat pengeluaran RM40, tetapi ia belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun saya. Apa yang perlu saya lakukan?

detailed.en: Hi boss, if you have made a withdrawal, please check your bank account. The withdrawal process usually takes 5-30 minutes. If it has been more than 30 minutes and it still hasn't been credited, you can send the transaction details to live chat for immediate checking. Also, check your wallet to see if the credit has been returned. If it still hasn't been credited, send the transaction details to live chat for immediate checking. We will assist you!
detailed.ms: Hai bos, jika anda telah membuat pengeluaran, sila semak akaun bank anda. Proses pengeluaran biasanya mengambil masa 5-30 minit. Jika sudah lebih 30 minit dan masih belum dikreditkan, anda boleh menghantar butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Juga, semak dalam wallet untuk melihat jika kredit telah dikembalikan. Jika masih belum masuk, hantarkan butiran transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Kami akan bantu anda!

question.text: What should I include in the online transfer for my JOKER ID?
variations: What details are needed for the online transfer?
How do I fill out the online transfer for my JOKER ID?

languages.en: What should I include in the online transfer for my JOKER ID?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya sertakan dalam pemindahan dalam talian untuk ID JOKER saya?

detailed.en: When making an online transfer, please ensure to fill in your JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' field along with other payment details. This is crucial for us to verify the receipt quickly.
detailed.ms: Apabila membuat pemindahan dalam talian, sila pastikan untuk mengisi ID JOKER anda dalam ruangan 'Rujukan Penerima' bersama dengan butiran pembayaran lain. Ini sangat penting untuk kami mengesahkan resit dengan cepat.

question.text: How can I make a fast payment using Touch 'n Go Fast Payment (FPX)?
variations: Nk bt mnm mna bos
Yaa fast pay

languages.en: How can I make a fast payment using Touch 'n Go Fast Payment (FPX)?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh membuat pembayaran cepat menggunakan Touch 'n Go Fast Payment (FPX)?

detailed.en: To top up using Touch 'n Go Fast Payment (FPX), follow these steps: 1. Go to the top-up page in the app. 2. Select 'Fast Payment (FPX)'. 3. Choose Touch 'n Go as the payment method. 4. Enter the top-up amount (Min RM50). 5. Confirm the transaction & complete the payment in the TNG app. 6. Wait 1-10 minutes for the system to automatically confirm the transaction. If it takes more than 10 minutes, please send the transaction receipt to live chat for verification.
detailed.ms: Untuk topup menggunakan Touch 'n Go Fast Payment (FPX), ikut langkah ini: 1. Pergi ke halaman topup dalam app. 2. Pilih 'Fast Payment (FPX)'. 3. Pilih Touch 'n Go sebagai kaedah pembayaran. 4. Masukkan jumlah topup (Min RM50). 5. Sahkan transaksi & lengkapkan pembayaran dalam app TNG. 6. Tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi secara automatik. Jika lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan.

detailed.en: To process a refund, you need to provide the correct account information to us. Please provide the account number and the name of the account holder as mentioned: - Bank Name: BANK ISLAM - Account Number: 13017028605463 - Account Holder Name: NADIATUL HUNSA BINTI MUDA. Ensure all this information is accurate to facilitate the refund process. If you need further assistance, let me know!

Sila berikan nombor akaun dan nama pemilik akaun yang betul, seperti yang anda sebutkan: - Nama Bank: BANK ISLAM - Nombor Akaun: 13017028605463 - Nama Pemilik: NADIATUL HUNSA BINTI MUDA. Pastikan semua maklumat ini tepat untuk memudahkan proses refund. Jika ada apa-apa lagi yang perlu dibantu, beritahu saya, ya!

question.text: What should I do if my top-up transaction is delayed?
variations: Why is my top-up taking so long?
How can I speed up my top-up process?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up transaction is delayed?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika transaksi top-up saya lewat?

detailed.en: Hi boss, once you've topped up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. After uploading, wait 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it hasn't been processed after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Hai boss, selepas top-up, pastikan resit sudah diupload ke halaman topup dalam aplikasi. Selepas upload, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem sahkan transaksi. Jika lebih 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran boss!

question.text: What should I do if my 4D winnings are delayed in being credited to my wallet?

languages.en: What should I do if my 4D winnings are delayed in being credited to my wallet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan 4D saya lambat dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: If your 4D winnings are delayed, please be patient as the system is processing. The winnings will be credited to your wallet automatically. You can check the 'Reports' section between 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM to see the credit. If it has been more than 30 minutes and the winnings have not appeared, please contact us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan 4D anda lambat, sila bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses. Kemenangan akan dikreditkan ke dalam dompet anda secara automatik. Anda boleh menyemak bahagian 'Laporan' antara 10:00 PM - 10:30 PM untuk melihat kredit tersebut. Jika lebih dari 30 minit dan kemenangan masih belum muncul, sila hubungi kami semula dengan tangkapan layar resit dan keputusan.

question.text: What should I do if my funds have not been credited to my account after making a deposit?
variations: Why hasn't my deposit been credited yet?

languages.en: What should I do if my funds have not been credited to my account after making a deposit?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika dana saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam akaun selepas membuat deposit?

detailed.en: If your funds have not been credited even after making a deposit, there may be a technical issue or an error with the receipt. Please wait around 3-10 minutes for the system to credit your account. If after 10 minutes it is still not credited, you can contact live chat for immediate assistance. Don't worry, you will be able to purchase numbers for the 9 PM draw once your account is credited.
detailed.ms: Jika dana anda belum masuk walaupun sudah bank in, mungkin ada masalah teknikal atau kesilapan dengan resit. Sila tunggu sekitar 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengkreditkan akaun anda. Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hubungi live chat untuk bantuan segera. Jangan risau, anda akan dapat membeli nombor untuk undian 9 malam setelah akaun anda dikreditkan.

detailed.en: If you forgot to include the correct reference on your deposit receipt, there is no problem. It may slow down the verification process a bit, but your funds are safe. Make sure to check the correct reference in the future. Also, remember to write the JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' every time you make a transfer.

Pastikan untuk semak rujukan yang tepat pada masa akan datang. Juga, ingat untuk menulis ID JOKER dalam 'Recipient Reference' setiap kali anda membuat pemindahan.

question.text: How can my friend log in to Joker if they are not receiving the TAC number?

detailed.en: If your friend is not receiving the TAC number to log in to JOKER, there are several steps they can try: 1. Check Phone Number: Ensure the registered phone number is correct and active. 2. Try Again: Ask your friend to resend the TAC request. 3. Check Signal: Make sure the phone has a good signal to receive messages. 4. Contact Support: If they still do not receive the TAC, it is best to contact customer support for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika kawan anda tidak menerima nombor TAC untuk log-in ke JOKER, ada beberapa langkah yang boleh dicuba: 1. Semak Nombor Telefon: Pastikan nombor telefon yang didaftarkan adalah betul dan aktif. 2. Cuba Lagi: Minta kawan anda untuk cuba menghantar semula permintaan TAC. 3. Semak Signal: Pastikan telefon mempunyai signal yang baik untuk menerima mesej. 4. Hubungi Sokongan: Jika masih tidak menerima TAC, lebih baik hubungi sokongan pelanggan untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What does AOS mean in the context of betting?
variations: What is AOS?
Can you explain AOS?

languages.en: What does AOS mean in the context of betting?
languages.ms: Apa maksud AOS dalam konteks pertaruhan?

detailed.en: AOS stands for Any Other Score, which refers to high scores that are not listed in the regular betting options. Examples of AOS scores include 5-0, 5-1, 5-2, 6-5, 3-7, 5-5, 6-6, and 10-10. Regardless of which team wins, if the final score is not on the list, it is counted as AOS. You can choose AOS in the Correct Score betting if you think the match will have an unexpected score.
detailed.ms: AOS bermaksud Any Other Score â€“ iaitu skor tinggi yang tidak disenaraikan dalam pilihan bet biasa. Contoh skor AOS termasuk 5-0, 5-1, 5-2, 6-5, 3-7, 5-5, 6-6, dan 10-10. Tak kira pasukan mana yang menang, jika skor akhir tidak ada dalam senarai, ia dikira sebagai AOS. Anda boleh memilih AOS dalam pertaruhan Correct Score jika anda rasa perlawanan akan ada skor luar jangka.

detailed.en: If your 3 ringgit top-up has not been credited yet, please wait for 10 minutes for the system to process. If it still does not appear, please contact live chat with your transaction details. After that, take a screenshot of our conversation and upload it in the top-up section of the app as a receipt. Don't forget to enter the amount of RM 13 during the upload. After submitting, wait for 1-10 minutes for the system to process the top-up. If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out to us in live chat!

question.text: What are the steps to top up using DuitNow and what should I be aware of during the process?

languages.ms: Apakah langkah-langkah untuk top up menggunakan DuitNow dan apa yang perlu saya perhatikan semasa proses tersebut?

detailed.en: To top up using DuitNow, follow these steps: 1. Open your banking app and select DuitNow Transfer. 2. Enter the company's account number and the correct amount (Min RM10 for ATM/Transfer, Min RM50 for Fast Payment). 3. Confirm the transaction and take a screenshot of the complete receipt. 4. Upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app, not in live chat. 5. Wait 3-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. Important: Ensure you use DuitNow Transfer (not regular eWallet transfer) and that the account owner's name matches the name in the app to avoid rejection. If you encounter any issues, please contact us via live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk top up menggunakan DuitNow, ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Buka aplikasi perbankan anda dan pilih Transfer DuitNow. 2. Masukkan nombor akaun syarikat dan jumlah yang betul (Min RM10 untuk ATM/Transfer, Min RM50 untuk Fast Payment). 3. Sahkan transaksi dan ambil tangkapan skrin resit yang lengkap. 4. Muat naik resit ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, bukan dalam live chat. 5. Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Penting: Pastikan menggunakan Transfer DuitNow (bukan transfer eWallet biasa) dan nama pemilik akaun mesti sepadan dengan nama dalam aplikasi untuk mengelakkan penolakan. Jika ada masalah, balas kepada kami dalam live chat ya!

question.text: What is the minimum amount required for withdrawal after topping up, and how does the turnover requirement work?
variations: Is the minimum withdrawal amount RM30?
How much do I need to withdraw after topping up?
What are the conditions for withdrawal?

languages.en: What is the minimum amount required for withdrawal after topping up, and how does the turnover requirement work?
languages.ms: Apakah jumlah minimum yang diperlukan untuk pengeluaran selepas top-up, dan bagaimana syarat turnover berfungsi?

detailed.en: The minimum amount for withdrawal is RM30. You need to achieve a 30% turnover from your deposit before you are eligible to withdraw. For example, if you top up RM100, you need to reach a turnover of RM130 (which is RM100 + 30%) before you can withdraw. If your balance is less than RM30, you will need to accumulate more before you can withdraw.
detailed.ms: Jumlah minimum untuk pengeluaran adalah RM30. Anda perlu mencapai 30% turnover daripada modal sebelum layak untuk mengeluarkan. Sebagai contoh, jika anda top-up RM100, anda perlu mencapai turnover RM130 (iaitu RM100 + 30%) sebelum boleh mengeluarkan. Jika baki anda kurang daripada RM30, anda perlu mengumpul lagi sebelum boleh mengeluarkan.

question.text: What should I do if the deposit name is different from the registered name for a refund?

languages.en: What should I do if the deposit name is different from the registered name for a refund?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika nama deposit berbeza dengan nama yang didaftarkan untuk pengembalian?

detailed.en: To process a refund when the deposit name differs from the registered name, please provide the account number and the name of the account holder. In this case, the account number is 08059023876047, and the account holder's name is Cik Nur Syaida Athirah Binti Ismail. The refund will be made to the account holder's name.
detailed.ms: Untuk memproses pengembalian apabila nama deposit berbeza daripada nama yang didaftarkan, sila berikan nombor akaun dan nama pemilik akaun. Dalam kes ini, nombor akaun adalah 08059023876047, dan nama pemilik akaun adalah Cik Nur Syaida Athirah Binti Ismail. Pengembalian akan dibuat kepada nama pemilik akaun.

question.text: How can I update my bank account details in the application?
variations: macam mana nak update account bank
update account bank
i want update account acc bank

languages.en: How can I update my bank account details in the application?
languages.ms: macam mana nak update account bank

detailed.en: To add a new bank account for withdrawal, follow these steps: 1. Open the app and tap on the Wallet icon. 2. Tap on Withdraw. 3. Tap on Add Account to enter your new bank account details. Ensure that the name on the bank account matches the registered profile. If you encounter any issues, please contact our live chat support for assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk menukar akaun bank dalam aplikasi, ikut langkah-langkah ini: 1. Buka aplikasi dan pergi ke bahagian 'Wallet'. 2. Pilih 'Withdraw'. 3. Klik pada 'Add Account' untuk memasukkan butiran akaun bank baru anda. Pastikan nama pada akaun bank sepadan dengan profil yang didaftarkan. Jika ada sebarang masalah, jangan ragu untuk hubungi sokongan live chat kami.

question.text: What should I do if I want to ensure my future deposits are processed correctly without issues related to account names?

detailed.en: In the future, please use your own bank account for transfers to avoid issues with refunds. If you continue to use a bank account under someone else's name, your transfer receipt will be burned, and no refunds will be issued. It is recommended to use FAST PAYMENT for deposits.

question.text: Why has my balance disappeared from my account?
variations: kenapa balance hilang?
apa sebab balance saya tiada?

languages.en: Why has my balance disappeared from my account?
languages.ms: Kenapa balance hilang dari akaun saya?

detailed.en: If your balance has disappeared, there could be several reasons. It might be that transactions have not been fully processed or there could be a technical issue. I recommend checking your account again, and if the problem persists, please contact our customer support for further assistance. Don't worry, we are here to help!
detailed.ms: Jika balance hilang, mungkin ada beberapa sebab. Mungkin transaksi belum diproses sepenuhnya atau ada masalah teknikal. Saya sarankan untuk memeriksa semula akaun anda dan jika masalah berterusan, sila hubungi sokongan pelanggan kami untuk bantuan lanjut. Jangan risau, kami sedia membantu!

question.text: How can I return the money I transferred to the wrong bank account?
variations: boleh kasih return balik ka duit tu?
macam mna la sya sudah tranfer pergi akaun yg slalu pakai itu hari
ya..saya bru tahu skrang..tp saya sudah ter tranfer pergi bank lama k@z itu..

languages.en: How can I return the money I transferred to the wrong bank account?
languages.ms: Boleh kasih return balik ka duit tu?

detailed.en: If you have mistakenly transferred money to the wrong bank account, unfortunately, the money cannot be refunded. However, you can still use the amount that has been credited for playing. Make sure to top-up correctly next time by uploading the bank-in slip through the app.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah tersalah transfer ke akaun yang salah, duit itu tidak boleh dipulangkan. Namun, anda masih boleh menggunakan jumlah yang telah dikreditkan untuk bermain. Pastikan untuk top-up dengan betul selepas ini dengan memuat naik slip bank-in melalui aplikasi.

question.text: What should I do if my transfer hasn't been credited yet after following the steps provided?
variations: What to do if my transfer is delayed?
How can I check the status of my transfer?
What steps should I take if my credit hasn't appeared?

languages.en: What should I do if my transfer hasn't been credited yet after following the steps provided?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pemindahan saya belum dikreditkan setelah mengikuti langkah-langkah yang diberikan?

detailed.en: If your credit hasn't been processed yet, it usually takes 3-10 minutes. Please check your transaction in the app first. If it has been more than 10 minutes and you still don't see the credit, please send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for further inspection. We will assist you as soon as possible! ğŸ˜ŠğŸ™
detailed.ms: Jika kredit anda belum diproses, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit. Sila semak transaksi anda dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu. Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan masih tiada kredit, sila hantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin! ğŸ˜ŠğŸ™

question.text: What steps should I follow to obtain a complete receipt from Maybank?

languages.en: What steps should I follow to obtain a complete receipt from Maybank?
languages.ms: Langkah-langkah apa yang perlu saya ikuti untuk mendapatkan resit lengkap dari Maybank?

detailed.en: To obtain a complete receipt from Maybank, please follow these steps: 1. Tap on 'Accounts'. 2. Select your bank account. 3. Tap on 'View Receipts'. 4. Click the download button as shown in the image. Ensure that the receipt you submit is complete as per the example provided. If you encounter any issues, please contact us via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Untuk mendapatkan resit lengkap dari Maybank, sila ikut langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Tekan 'Akaun'. 2. Pilih akaun bank anda. 3. Tekan 'Lihat Resit'. 4. Klik butang muat turun seperti yang ditunjukkan dalam gambar. Pastikan resit yang anda hantar lengkap seperti contoh yang diberikan. Jika anda menghadapi sebarang masalah, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if I have already deposited money into my account but it hasn't reflected yet?
variations: What if my deposit isn't showing up?
What to do if the money is deducted but not credited?

languages.en: What should I do if I have already deposited money into my account but it hasn't reflected yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya sudah mendepositkan wang ke dalam akaun saya tetapi ia belum dipaparkan?

detailed.en: If the money has been deducted from your bank account but the deposit hasn't been successful, there may be a technical issue or an error with the receipt/transaction. Try to deposit again or send the receipt via live chat for further verification. If there's anything else I can assist you with, just let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika duit telah ditolak dari akaun bank tetapi deposit tak berjaya, mungkin ada masalah teknikal atau kesilapan dengan resit/transaksi. Cuba buat deposit semula atau hantar resit melalui live chat untuk semakan lanjut. Jika ada apa-apa yang boleh saya bantu, beritahu saja!

question.text: What should I do to top up my account using the banking app provided?

languages.en: What should I do to top up my account using the banking app provided?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan untuk menambah nilai akaun saya menggunakan aplikasi perbankan yang disediakan?

detailed.en: Please use the bank account provided in your app for banking. Make sure to check the bank account in your app before topping up. Do not save the bank account as a favorite. Also, ensure that you do not upload the same receipt again, as it may slow down the system.
detailed.ms: Sila gunakan akaun bank yang disediakan dalam aplikasi anda untuk perbankan. Pastikan anda menyemak akaun bank dalam aplikasi anda sebelum menambah nilai. Jangan simpan akaun bank sebagai kegemaran. Juga, pastikan anda tidak memuat naik resit yang sama lagi, kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem.

question.text: What should I do if I accidentally shared credit with the wrong ID?
variations: What happens if I share credit with the wrong ID?
How can I recover credit shared with the wrong ID?

languages.en: What should I do if I accidentally shared credit with the wrong ID?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya secara tidak sengaja berkongsi kredit dengan ID yang salah?

detailed.en: If you have shared credit with the wrong ID, unfortunately, the system cannot automatically return it. You can take the following steps: 1. Provide the wrong JOKER ID you shared and the amount of credit involved. 2. We will try to contact the owner of that ID and request them to return the credit in the same way (Share Credit). 3. However, there is no guarantee that the credit can be returned, as it depends on the owner of the ID who received it. In the future, please ensure that the ID entered is correct before pressing send.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah berkongsi kredit dengan ID yang salah, malangnya, sistem tidak dapat memulangkan secara automatik. Anda boleh mengambil langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Berikan JOKER ID yang anda kongsi secara salah dan jumlah kredit yang terlibat. 2. Kami akan cuba menghubungi pemilik ID tersebut dan meminta mereka untuk mengembalikan kredit dengan cara yang sama (Kongsi Kredit). 3. Namun, tiada jaminan kredit dapat dikembalikan, ia bergantung kepada pemilik ID yang menerimanya. Lain kali, pastikan ID yang dimasukkan adalah betul sebelum menekan hantar.

question.text: What should I do if my 4D winnings have not been credited to my wallet yet?

languages.en: What should I do if my 4D winnings have not been credited to my wallet yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan 4D saya belum dikreditkan ke dalam dompet saya?

detailed.en: If you have won a 4D number, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little time today. The winnings will be automatically credited to your wallet. Please check the app from time to time. If it has been more than 30 minutes and the winnings have still not been credited, you can contact us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.
detailed.ms: Jika anda mempunyai nombor 4D yang menang, mohon bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses dan mungkin mengambil sedikit masa hari ini. Duit kemenangan akan dikreditkan secara automatik ke dalam dompet anda. Sila semak aplikasi dari semasa ke semasa. Jika lebih dari 30 minit dan duit kemenangan masih belum dikreditkan, anda boleh menghubungi kami semula dengan tangkapan skrin resit dan keputusan.

question.text: What should I do if I cannot send the receipt for my transaction?
variations: How can I send the receipt if I'm having trouble?
What steps can I take to successfully upload my receipt?

languages.en: What should I do if I cannot send the receipt for my transaction?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya tidak dapat menghantar resit untuk transaksi saya?

detailed.en: If you are unable to send the receipt, you can try the following steps: 1. Restart your phone or close and reopen the app. 2. Try switching your internet connection (from WiFi to mobile data or vice versa). 3. Ensure your internet connection is stable before trying again. If the problem persists, you can send the receipt directly to live chat for further assistance. We will help process it for you!
detailed.ms: Jika anda tidak dapat menghantar resit, mungkin anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah ini: 1. Mulakan semula telefon anda atau tutup dan buka semula aplikasi. 2. Cuba tukar rangkaian internet (WiFi ke data mudah alih atau sebaliknya). 3. Pastikan sambungan internet anda stabil sebelum mencuba lagi. Jika masalah masih berterusan, anda boleh hantarkan resit terus ke live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu prosesnya untuk anda!

question.text: What should I do if my deposit is taking too long to process?

languages.en: What should I do if my deposit is taking too long to process?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika deposit saya mengambil masa terlalu lama untuk diproses?

detailed.en: If your deposit is taking too long, it usually takes between 5 to 30 minutes. If you feel like you are waiting too long, please let me know, and I will check it for you!
detailed.ms: Jika deposit anda lambat masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa antara 5 hingga 30 minit. Jika anda rasa tunggu terlalu lama, beritahu saya, dan saya akan semak untuk anda!

question.text: What should I do if I have topped up but my transaction has not been confirmed in the app?

languages.en: What should I do if I have topped up but my transaction has not been confirmed in the app?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya telah topup tetapi transaksi saya belum disahkan dalam aplikasi?

detailed.en: Hi boss, once you have topped up, make sure to upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. ğŸ˜Š After uploading, wait 1-10 minutes for the system to confirm the transaction. If it still hasn't appeared after 10 minutes, you can send the transaction receipt to live chat for immediate verification. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Hai bos, setelah anda topup, pastikan resit telah dimuat naik ke halaman topup dalam aplikasi. ğŸ˜Š Selepas memuat naik, tunggu 1-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi. Jika selepas 10 minit masih belum masuk, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi ke live chat untuk semakan segera. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: What should I do to ensure a smooth top-up process using the banking app?

languages.en: What should I do to ensure a smooth top-up process using the banking app?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan untuk memastikan proses top-up berjalan lancar menggunakan aplikasi perbankan?

detailed.en: To ensure a smooth top-up process, please follow the list of banks provided in the app for your transfers. Make sure to use the account displayed on the top-up page to avoid any issues. Additionally, do not save our bank account as a favorite, as the account number may change from time to time. If you have any other questions, feel free to contact us via live chat.
detailed.ms: Untuk memastikan proses top-up berjalan lancar, sila ikut senarai bank yang disediakan dalam aplikasi untuk pemindahan anda. Pastikan anda menggunakan akaun yang tertera pada halaman top-up untuk mengelakkan sebarang masalah. Selain itu, jangan simpan akaun bank kami sebagai kegemaran, kerana nombor akaun mungkin akan berubah dari semasa ke semasa. Jika anda mempunyai sebarang pertanyaan lain, sila hubungi kami melalui live chat.

question.text: What should I do if I am having trouble logging in to my account?
variations: How can I resolve login issues?
What steps can I take if I can't log in?

languages.en: What should I do if I am having trouble logging in to my account?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya menghadapi masalah untuk log masuk ke akaun saya?

detailed.en: If you are having trouble logging in, you can try the following steps: 1. Ensure that your username and password are correct. 2. Try clearing your browser's cache and cookies. 3. If it still doesn't work, try using a different browser or mobile app. If you continue to have issues, please let me know!
detailed.ms: Jika anda mengalami masalah untuk log masuk, anda boleh cuba langkah-langkah berikut: 1. Pastikan nama pengguna dan kata laluan anda betul. 2. Cuba kosongkan cache dan cookies pelayar anda. 3. Jika masih tidak berjaya, cuba gunakan pelayar lain atau aplikasi mudah alih. Jika anda masih menghadapi masalah, beritahu saya ya!

question.text: What should I do to top up my account using the banking app provided?

languages.en: What should I do to top up my account using the banking app provided?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan untuk menambah nilai akaun saya menggunakan aplikasi perbankan yang disediakan?

detailed.en: Please use the bank account provided in your app for banking. Make sure to check the bank account in your app before topping up. Do not save the bank account as a favorite.
detailed.ms: Sila gunakan akaun bank yang disediakan dalam aplikasi anda untuk perbankan. Pastikan anda menyemak akaun bank dalam aplikasi anda sebelum menambah nilai. Jangan simpan akaun bank sebagai kegemaran.

question.text: What should I do if my funds haven't been credited after uploading the bank slip?
variations: Why hasn't my money come in yet?
What is the status of my top-up?
How long does it take for the funds to be credited?

languages.en: What should I do if my funds haven't been credited after uploading the bank slip?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika dana saya belum dikreditkan selepas memuat naik slip bank?

detailed.en: If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds have not been credited, please send a screenshot of your receipt. I will assist in checking immediately. Thank you!
detailed.ms: Jika sudah lebih 10 minit dan dana masih belum masuk, sila hantar tangkapan skrin resit anda. Saya akan bantu semak dengan segera. Terima kasih!

question.text: What should I do after uploading the receipt?

languages.en: What should I do after uploading the receipt?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan selepas memuat naik resit?

detailed.en: The receipt has been successfully uploaded. Please wait a moment for the system to process it. Do not upload the same receipt again as it may slow down the system. Thank you for your patience and cooperation!
detailed.ms: Resit telah berjaya dimuat naik. Sila tunggu sebentar untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jangan muat naik resit yang sama lagi kerana ia mungkin melambatkan sistem. Terima kasih atas kesabaran dan kerjasama anda!

question.text: Hi, is there a delay in receiving notifications for the 4D winnings tonight?
variations: Why haven't I received any notifications?
Is there a problem with the notification system?

languages.en: Hi, is there a delay in receiving notifications for the 4D winnings tonight?
languages.ms: Hai, adakah terdapat kelewatan dalam menerima pemberitahuan untuk kemenangan 4D malam ini?

detailed.en: If you have won a 4D number, please be patient as the system is processing and it may take a little time today. The winnings will automatically be credited to your wallet, so please check from time to time in the app.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah menang nombor 4D, mohon bersabar kerana sistem sedang memproses dan mungkin mengambil sedikit masa hari ini. Duit kemenangan akan dimasukkan secara automatik ke dalam wallet anda, jadi sila semak dari semasa ke semasa dalam aplikasi.

question.text: What should I do if my payment has not been received after topping up via Fast Payment (FPX)?
variations: What if my payment is delayed?
How long should I wait for my payment to be processed?

languages.en: What should I do if my payment has not been received after topping up via Fast Payment (FPX)?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika pembayaran saya belum diterima selepas topup melalui Fast Payment (FPX)?

detailed.en: If you have topped up via Fast Payment (FPX), please wait for 10 minutes as the system is processing. Typically, the funds should be credited within 1-10 minutes. If it has been more than 10 minutes and the funds are still not received, please send a complete transaction receipt to live chat for further verification.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah topup melalui Fast Payment (FPX), mohon tunggu 10 minit kerana sistem sedang memproses. Biasanya, dana akan dimasukkan dalam 1-10 minit. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan dana masih belum diterima, sila hantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk semakan lanjut.

question.text: Why is my game crediting slower than usual after topping up?
variations: Game dah nk start
Selalu cepat masok. Sekarang banyak slow

languages.en: Why is my game crediting slower than usual after topping up?
languages.ms: Mengapa kredit permainan saya lebih lambat daripada biasa selepas topup?

detailed.en: Typically, winnings are credited automatically within 5 to 30 minutes. However, sometimes it can take longer due to a high volume of transactions. If your winnings have not been credited within that time frame, please be patient or contact live chat support for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Biasanya, kemenangan akan dikreditkan secara automatik dalam masa 5 hingga 30 minit. Namun, kadang-kadang ia boleh mengambil masa lebih lama disebabkan oleh jumlah transaksi yang tinggi. Jika kemenangan anda belum dikreditkan dalam tempoh itu, sila bersabar atau hubungi sokongan live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited yet?
variations: Bos top Up belom masok
What to do if top-up is delayed?

languages.en: What should I do if my top-up has not been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika top-up saya belum dikreditkan?

detailed.en: If your top-up has not been credited yet, it usually takes 3-10 minutes to process. Please check the transaction in the app first. If it has been more than 10 minutes and it is still not credited, please send the complete transaction receipt to live chat support for further inspection. We will assist you as soon as possible!
detailed.ms: Jika top-up anda belum masuk, biasanya ia mengambil masa 3-10 minit untuk diproses. Sila semak transaksi dalam aplikasi terlebih dahulu. Jika sudah lebih dari 10 minit dan masih belum dikreditkan, sila hantarkan resit transaksi lengkap kepada sokongan live chat untuk pemeriksaan lanjut. Kami akan bantu secepat mungkin!

question.text: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited yet?
variations: Belum masuk
Nanti Singapore tutup

languages.en: What should I do if my winnings have not been credited yet?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika kemenangan saya belum dimasukkan?

detailed.en: If your winnings have not been credited yet, please wait around 10 minutes for the system to process it. If it still does not appear, please contact live chat support with your transaction details. I hope it gets resolved quickly!
detailed.ms: Jika kemenangan anda belum dimasukkan, sila tunggu sekitar 10 minit untuk sistem memprosesnya. Jika masih tidak muncul, sila hubungi sokongan live chat dengan butiran transaksi anda. Semoga cepat selesai!

question.text: I mistakenly entered the wrong amount while submitting my payment. How can I correct this?
variations: I entered the wrong amount
How do I fix my payment submission error?

languages.en: I mistakenly entered the wrong amount while submitting my payment. How can I correct this?
languages.ms: Saya tersilap memasukkan jumlah yang salah semasa menghantar pembayaran saya. Bagaimana saya boleh membetulkannya?

detailed.en: If you have banked in RM33 but it shows RM50, there may have been an error in the process. Please ensure that the amount entered matches your receipt. If there are any issues, you can send the receipt via live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah bank in RM33 tetapi tertulis RM50, mungkin ada kesilapan dalam proses. Pastikan jumlah yang dimasukkan sepadan dengan resit anda. Jika ada masalah, anda boleh hantar resit melalui live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

question.text: How can I withdraw money from my account using the application?
variations: mau withdraw bos

languages.en: How can I withdraw money from my account using the application?
languages.ms: Mau withdraw bos

detailed.en:
To withdraw money, follow these steps in the application:

If you have any issues or need assistance, reply to us in live chat!
detailed.ms:
Untuk melakukan pengeluaran, ikut langkah-langkah ini dalam aplikasi:

1ï¸âƒ£ Klik ikon 'Wallet' (di tengah bawah skrin).
2ï¸âƒ£ Pilih 'Withdraw'.

question.text: How can I top up my account with RM50 and what should I do if I entered the wrong amount?
variations: What are the steps to top up RM50?

languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top up akaun saya dengan RM50 dan apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika saya memasukkan amaun yang salah?

detailed.en: To top up your account with RM50, you can follow these steps: For ATM/Transfer (minimum RM10), use Instant Transfer or DuitNow, enter the correct company account number and amount, write your JOKER ID in the 'Recipient Reference' if using online banking, upload the receipt in the top-up page of the app, and wait for 3-10 minutes for processing. For Fast Payment (FPX) (minimum RM50, faster), go to the top-up page in the app, select Fast Payment (FPX) and your bank, enter the amount and confirm the transaction, and wait for 1-3 minutes for automatic confirmation. Ensure the bank account name matches the name in the app. If you entered the wrong amount, wait for the system to automatically reject the receipt, then upload the same receipt again but this time enter the correct amount. If you have any other issues, feel free to contact us.
detailed.ms: Untuk top up akaun anda dengan RM50, anda boleh mengikuti langkah-langkah ini: Untuk ATM/Transfer (minimum RM10), gunakan Instant Transfer atau DuitNow, masukkan nombor akaun syarikat dan amaun yang betul, tulis JOKER ID anda dalam 'Recipient Reference' jika menggunakan perbankan dalam talian, muat naik resit di halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, dan tunggu 3-10 minit untuk proses. Untuk Fast Payment (FPX) (minimum RM50, lebih cepat), pergi ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi, pilih Fast Payment (FPX) dan bank anda, masukkan amaun dan sahkan transaksi, dan tunggu 1-3 minit untuk pengesahan automatik. Pastikan nama akaun bank sepadan dengan nama dalam aplikasi. Jika anda memasukkan amaun yang salah, tunggu sistem menolak resit secara automatik, kemudian muat naik semula resit yang sama tetapi kali ini masukkan amaun yang betul. Jika anda mempunyai masalah lain, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi kami.

detailed.en: If you have submitted the same receipt twice, don't worry! The system only requires one receipt for verification. Submitting the same receipt multiple times may cause your application to be rejected. Please wait 3-10 minutes for processing. If you encounter any issues, feel free to reply to us in live chat.

If it has been more than 30 minutes and it is still not credited, please contact us again with a screenshot of the receipt and result.
detailed.ms: Jika bayaran atau top-up anda belum dikreditkan, sila tunggu antara 3 hingga 10 minit selepas memuat naik resit. Jika masih tiada, anda boleh menghantar tangkapan skrin resit kepada saya dan saya akan bantu semak dengan segera. Selain itu, jika anda menang nombor 4D, mohon sabar ya â€” sistem sedang proses dan mungkin ambil masa sikit hari ni. Duit menang akan masuk ke wallet anda secara automatik, jadi sila semak dalam aplikasi dari semasa ke semasa. Jika lebih 30 minit masih belum masuk, boleh hubungi kami semula dengan tangkapan skrin resit & keputusan.

question.text: What should I do if my transaction status shows PENDING and I am experiencing delays in processing?

languages.en: What should I do if my transaction status shows PENDING and I am experiencing delays in processing?
languages.ms: Apa yang perlu saya lakukan jika status transaksi saya menunjukkan PENDING dan saya mengalami kelewatan dalam pemprosesan?

detailed.en: If your transaction status shows PENDING, it means the system is currently processing. Please wait until the system completes the process. Do not upload the receipt multiple times as it will slow down the process. If it takes more than 10 minutes and the status is still PENDING, you can send the complete transaction receipt to live chat for further checking. Thank you for your patience!
detailed.ms: Jika status transaksi anda menunjukkan PENDING, ini bermakna sistem sedang memproses. Sila tunggu sehingga sistem selesai memproses. Jangan muat naik resit banyak kali kerana ia akan melambatkan proses. Jika lebih dari 10 minit dan status masih PENDING, anda boleh menghantar resit transaksi lengkap ke live chat untuk semakan lanjut. Terima kasih atas kesabaran anda!

question.text: How can I top up my e-wallet using Touch 'n Go?
variations: I boleh topu e wallet

languages.en: How can I top up my e-wallet using Touch 'n Go?
languages.ms: Bagaimana saya boleh top-up e-wallet saya menggunakan Touch 'n Go?

detailed.en:
To top-up using Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet, follow these steps:

1ï¸âƒ£ Open the TNG eWallet app.
2ï¸âƒ£ Select 'DuitNow Transfer' for manual method or 'Fast Payment (FPX)' for quicker transactions.
3ï¸âƒ£ Enter the company's bank account number (refer to the top-up page in the app).
4ï¸âƒ£ Enter the top-up amount (min RM10 for DuitNow, min RM50 for FPX).
5ï¸âƒ£ Confirm the transaction and take a screenshot of the receipt.
6ï¸âƒ£ If using DuitNow, upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app.
7ï¸âƒ£ Wait 3-10 minutes for transaction confirmation.

ğŸ“Œ Important:
âœ… Ensure the account owner's name matches the name in the app to avoid rejection.

If you encounter any issues, please reply to us in live chat!
detailed.ms:
Untuk top-up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) eWallet, ikut langkah-langkah ini:

1ï¸âƒ£ Buka aplikasi TNG eWallet.
2ï¸âƒ£ Pilih 'DuitNow Transfer' jika anda ingin menggunakan kaedah manual, atau pilih 'Fast Payment (FPX)' untuk transaksi yang lebih cepat.
3ï¸âƒ£ Masukkan nombor akaun bank syarikat (rujuk pada halaman top-up dalam aplikasi).
4ï¸âƒ£ Masukkan jumlah top-up (min RM10 untuk DuitNow, min RM50 untuk FPX).
5ï¸âƒ£ Sahkan transaksi dan ambil tangkapan skrin resit.
6ï¸âƒ£ Jika menggunakan DuitNow, muat naik resit ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi.
7ï¸âƒ£ Tunggu 3-10 minit untuk pengesahan transaksi.

ğŸ“Œ Penting:
âœ… Pastikan nama pemilik akaun sepadan dengan nama dalam aplikasi untuk mengelakkan penolakan.

Jika ada sebarang masalah, balas kepada kami dalam live chat ya!
